quran[856]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Twa, Siiyn, Miiym, (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  26,2,Aya n’amajambo ari mugitabu kimenyesha ibikenewe bijanye n’idini
  26,3,Nkumbure wota umutima wawe murudubi kubera abantu bawe batabaye aba Isilamu
  26,4,Iyo dushaka twari kubamanurira ibitangaro bivuye mw’ijuru hanyuma amazosi yabo akagamburuka nugukurikira bashaka canke badashaka mugabo ntidushaka kutegeka umuntu ngo abe umu Isilamu
  26,5,"Mugabo\tntibashikirwa\tn’icibutso\tgishasha\tkivuye\tkuri\tnyene\timigisha myinshi, mugabo yama ija kure yivyo"
  26,6,"Rero mu vy’ukuri barahakanye kuri ivyo rero ubu vuba, bazoshikirwa n’inkuru z’ivyo bahora bajajurirako"
  26,7,Mbega ntibabonye ngaha kw’Isi ingene twanagishije ibiterwa biri kuriyo n’ubwoko butandukanye bwiza
  26,8,Ntankeka muri ivyo harimwo ibimenyetso mugabo benshi muribo ntavyo bemera
  26,9,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,10,"N’Umuremyi\twawe\tmugihe\tyahamagara\tintumwa\tyiwe\tMussa\t(iiii) amubwira ati:- nugende kuri barya bantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  26,11,"Abantu bo kwa Fir’auni ubabwire uti:- mbega ntibatinya Imana"
  26,12,"Nawe avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje mu vy’ukuri jewe ndatinya yuko abo bantu bompakana"
  26,13,"N’igikiriza canje ntiki nyorohereza hamwe n’ururimi wanje ntirutomora amajambo neza, rero nushikirize ubu butumwa kwa mwene wanje Haruna (iii)"
  26,14,Nabo n’abantu bafise amakosa imbere yanje mugabo ntinya yuko bongandagura
  26,15,"Avuga ati:- Oya sivyo, ahubwo ni mugende n’ibi bitangaro vyanje, mu vy’ukuri twebwe turi kumwe namwe kandi turabumva"
  26,16,"Rero nimugende kwa Fir’auni mumubwire muti:- ntankeka twebwe turi intumwa z’Umuremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,17,Turungitswe yuko wobatwarira turi kumwe twese hamwe na bene Israeri
  26,18,"Fir’auni aca avuga ati:- mbega wewe ntitwakurereye iwacu muugihe wari ukiri mutoyi hanyuma turabana twese kumyaka myinshi y’ubuzima bwawe bwose"
  26,19,Kandi waragize ico gikorwa cawe muvyo wagize vyose uca uba mu bantu badashima
  26,20,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ivuga iti:- naragize ivyo vyose ngaho mugihe nari mu bantu bazimiye"
  26,21,Rero nanje naciye ndabahunga mugihe natinya Umuremyi wanje ubu yarampaye amategeko kandi yarampezagiye ngombe ndi muntumwa z’Imana
  26,22,Kandi uwo niwo mugisha wangiriyeko impuhwe wukubashira mubuja wa bene Israeri
  26,23,"Fir’auni yavuze ati:- ni nde uyo Muremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,24,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa ivuga iti :- n’Umuremyi w’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe nibirimwo nimwaba mwebwe muri mu bantu mwemera"
  26,25,"Fir’aauni\tyabwiye\tabantu\tbamukikuje\tati :-\tmbega\tmwebwe ntimwumva"
  26,26,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) aca avuga ati:- Umuremyi niwe muremyi w’abavyeyi banyu baho hambere"
  26,27,"Fir’auni aca avuga ati:- ntankeka iyo ntumwa yanyu yarungitswe kuri mwebwe n’umusazi"
  26,28,"Intumwa\ty’Imana\tMussa\t(iii)\tivuga\titi:-\tUmuremyi\tw’ubuseruko n’uburengera zuba hamwe n’ibiri hagati yavyo nimwaba mutegera neza"
  26,29,"Fir’auni aca avuga ati:- niwakurikira iyindi Mana atari jewe mu vy’ukuri nzokugira nk’abantu bari mwibohero"
  26,30,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ivuga iti:- mbega naho nokuzanira ikintu kiri k’umugaragaro"
  26,31,"Fir’auni nawe amwishura ati:- nukizane niwaba uri mu bantu bavugisha ukuri kwama"
  26,32,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ica ijugunya inkoni yiwe, mukanya isase ica ihinduka inzoka nyakuri iri k’umugaragaro"
  26,33,Ica isokorora ukuboko kwayo mumpuzu mumwanya isase guca kurera derere kubantu bakubonye
  26,34,"Fir’auni\tavuga\tabwira\tabakuru\tbamukikuje\tati :-\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tuyu n’umurozi afise ubumenyi buhanitse"
  26,35,"Agomba\tabakure\tmugihugu\tcanyu\takoresheje\tuburozi\tbwiwe,\tnone mwebwe mubivuga ko iki"
  26,36,"Nabo\tbavuga\tbati:-\tnimumuhe\tumwanya\thamwe\tna\tmwene\twabo hanyuma mubarungike mugisagara caho bakoraniriza abantu bose"
  26,37,Bazokuzanira ibihangange vy’abarozi bose bafise ubumenyi buhanitse
  26,38,"Barakoranijwe\tabarozi\tbose,\tmumwanya\tn’umusi\twagenewe\turwo rubanza"
  26,39,"Baca babwirwa abantu bati :- none mwese mwamaze gukorana"
  26,40,Nkumbure tuzobakurikira abo barozi niba aribo bazoronka intsinzi
  26,41,"Rero mugihe bashika abo barozi baciye babwira Fir’auni bati:- mbega turaronka impembo nitwa tahukana intsinzi"
  26,42,"Fir’auni abishura ati:- egome kandi mwebwe muzoba muri bamwe mu bantu banje bizigirwa"
  26,43,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ibabwira babarozi iti:- nimujugunye ivyo mushobora kujugunya"
  26,44,"Bajugunya imigozi yabo hamwe n’inkoni zabo nukuvuga bati:- kububasha bwa Fir’auni ni twebwe bene intsinzi"
  26,45,Hanyuma intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ica ijugunya inkoni yayo hasi yankoni ica iramiragura ivyo abo barozi badukanye
  26,46,Aho niho babarozi bose barwa hasi barapfukama
  26,47,"Baca bavuga bati:- turemeye Umuremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,48,Umuremyi wa Mussa (iii) hamwe na Haruna (iii)
  26,49,"Fir’auni avuga ati:- mbega mwamwemeye uyo Mussa (iii) imbere yuko ndabaha uruhusha? Ntankeka niwe yabaye umukuru wanyu yabigishije uburozi, ubu rero muzotahura neza, ubu ngiye gucagagura amaboko n’amaguru yanyu ndabitandukanije hanyuma nce ndababamba kubiti mwese"
  26,50,"Nabo baca bavuga bati:- ntaco bitwaye mu vy’ukuri twese tuzo subira ku Muremyi wacu"
  26,51,"Ntankeka twebwe twizeye yuko Umuremyi wacu azotugirira ikigongwe kubera ibicumuro vyacu, kuko twebwe tubaye abambere mukwemera kuba aba Isilamu b’ukuri"
  26,52,"Twara\tmurungikiye\tintumwa\ty’Imana\tMussa\t(iii)\tubutumire\tyuko yogenda ku bantu banje mugihe c’ijoro ntankeka muzo kurikiranwa"
  26,53,"Rero\tFir’auni\tyaciye\tarungika\tubutumwa\tbw’ugukoranya\tabantu\tbo mugisagara bose"
  26,54,Mu vy’ukuri abo Bayahudi n’akarwi k’abantu bakeyi cane
  26,55,Nabo n’abantu badu shavuza cane
  26,56,Natwe turi benshi mugabo turabatinya
  26,57,Duca tubakura mu mirima yabo hamwe no mumusoko y’amazi
  26,58,Nukuba kura mububiko bwabo n’ahantu habo heza cane
  26,59,Nuko rero twahaye ibisigi kuri bene Israeri
  26,60,Baca bakurikira k’ubuseruko bw’izuba
  26,61,"Mugihe zabonana ingabo zose uko ari zibiri, abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) baciye bavuga bati:- twebwe duhava dufatwa"
  26,62,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ica ivuga iti:- oya! mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wanje ari kumwe nanje ntankeka azondongora"
  26,63,"Mumwanya twara murungikiye intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ubutumwa tumubwira duti:- kubita iyo nkoni yawe kuri ico kiyaga, naco gica cigaburwamwo ibiyaga bibiri no kumpande zose haca haba nk’imisozi mininiya"
  26,64,Duca tuzana ngaho abandi bantu
  26,65,Duca turokora intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe nabo bari kumwe bose
  26,66,Hanyuma twibiza mumazi abo bandi bantu
  26,67,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tmuri\tibi\tvyose\tharimwo\ticirwa\tmugabo\tbenshi\tmuribo simubemera"
  26,68,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,69,Kandi ubasomere inkuru y’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)
  26,70,"Mugihe yabwira Se wiwe hamwe n’abantu biwe ati:- mbega\tmwebwe musenga ibiki"
  26,71,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- twebwe dusenga amasanamu yamisi yose"
  26,72,"Nawe avuga ati:- mbega ayo masanamu musenga arabumva mugihe muyahamagaye"
  26,73,Canke harico abamarira canke abagirira inabi
  26,74,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- ahubwo twasanze badata bacu bagira uku nyene tugira"
  26,75,"Nawe abishura ati:- mbega mwarababonye abo musenga"
  26,76,Mwebwe hamwe n’abavyeyi banyu babayeho imbere yanyu
  26,77,Ntankeka abo n’abansi banje dukuyemwo Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  26,78,Kuko ariyo yandemye kandi niyo yandongoye
  26,79,Kandi niyo intamika nukunywesha
  26,80,No mugihe nsinzikajwe n’ingwara niyo indonsa akoyokwe
  26,81,Kandi niyo izonyica hanyuma ize insubize ubuzima
  26,82,Kandi niyo nizeye yuko izongirira ikigongwe kubicumuro vyanje k’umusi w’impembo
  26,83,"Muremyi wanje numpe itegeko, kandi umpuze n’abagira ibikorwa vyiza"
  26,84,Kandi umpezagire mukuvugwa kuneza n’abantu bazoza munyuma yanje
  26,85,Kandi umpezagire mubazosigirwa ibisigi vy’imirima irimwo imihezagiro myiza yo mw’ijuru
  26,86,Kandi ugirire ikigongwe Data wanje ntankeka yari mubantu bazimiye
  26,87,Kandi ntuntetereze k’umusi wukuzurwa kw’abantu bose
  26,88,Umusi waho amatungo yabo ataco azobamarira canke ibibondo vyabo
  26,89,Dukuyemwo uwuzoba yatumbereye Imana yiwe afise umutima mwiza
  26,90,N’ijuru rizokwegerezwa ribe hafi ku bantu beranda
  26,91,N’umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu uzokwerekanwa icese kubagizi b’inabi
  26,92,"Bazobwirwa bati:- bari hehe abo mwahora musenga"
  26,93,Atari Imana mbega boshobora kubafasha canke kwifashisha bonyene
  26,94,Rero bazotabwa mumuriro udahera hamwe n’abacumuzi bagenzi babo
  26,95,Hamwe n’ingabo za Shetani zose
  26,96,Bazovuga bamwe bahora babasenga mugihe bazoba bariko baratongana bari mumuriro udahera
  26,97,"Ndarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana, mu vy’ukuri twebwe twari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  26,98,Mugihe twabagirira ineza n’Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  26,99,Kandi ntibatuzimije atari babantu babi
  26,100,Natwe ntidufise abadusabira
  26,101,Canke abagenzi bwite dufise
  26,102,Iyo tuba dufise aho tugarukira twari kuba aba Isilamu
  26,103,"Ntankeka\tmuri\tibi\tvyose\tharimwo\titegero\trininiya\tmugabo\tbenshi muribo s’abemera"
  26,104,Mu vy’ukuri umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,105,Abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,106,"Ubibutse mugihe yababwira uwo mugenzi wabo ariwe Nuhu (iii) ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimuzotinya"
  26,107,Mu vyukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,108,Rero nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri kandi mungamburukire
  26,109,"Kandi\tsindabashakira\tko\timpembo,\tmugabo\timpembo\tyanje\tiri k’umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,110,Rero nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri kandi mungamburukire
  26,111,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- mbega tukwemere wewe mugihe abagowe aribo bagukurikira"
  26,112,"Nawe avuga ati:- nomenya gute ibikorwa vyanyu mwahora mugira"
  26,113,Iharurwa ryabo ntarihari atari ku muremyi wanje gusa iyo mwobimenya
  26,114,Nanje sinzo kwirukana abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  26,115,"Jewe ntaco ndimwo, atari uko ndimubatuza bari k’umugaragaro"
  26,116,"Nabo bavuga bati:- nutareka ewe Nuhu (iii) iryo tuza ryawe ntankeka uzoba uri mubazoterwa amabuye"
  26,117,"Nawe avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, ntankeka abantu banje banyihakanye"
  26,118,"Rero nuducire urubanza ruri hagati yanje hamwe nabo, urwo rubanza rube rwiza, kandi undokore hamwe nabo ndikumwe nabo hamwe n’abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  26,119,Kubera ivyo twaciye tumurokora hamwe nabo bari kumwe bose bari mubwato bwari butwaye ibintu vyinshi
  26,120,Hanyuma twibiza mumazi mubasigaye
  26,121,Ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mubemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  26,122,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tnyene\tububasha\tn’impuhwe zihagije"
  26,123,Na bene Aadi nabo barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,124,"Mugihe\tmwene\twabo\tHudu\t(iii)\tyababwira\tati:-\tmbega\tmwebwe ntimuzotinya Imana yanyu"
  26,125,Ntankeka jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,126,"Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, kandi mungamburukire"
  26,127,"Kandi\tntaco\tnshaka\tkuri\tibi\tvyose,\tmugabo\timpembo\tyanje\tiri\tku muremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,128,"Mbega mwiyubakira amazu ahari agatumba, uku n’ugufyinata muriko muragira"
  26,129,Mukiyubakira n’inzitiro nk’uko mubona yuko muzoramba mubuzima bwanyu bwose
  26,130,No mugihe muteye abandi mubatera n’ubwishime
  26,131,Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri kandi mungamburukire
  26,132,Nimutinye uwabahaye ibi vyose muzi
  26,133,Ko ariwe yabahaye ibikoko hamwe n’ibibondo vy’abahungu
  26,134,Hamwe n’imirima n’amasoko y’amazi n’inzuzi
  26,135,Mu vy’ukuri ndabafitiye ubwoba bw’ibihano vy’umusi w’imperuka
  26,136,"Nabo bamwishuye bati:- n’ibisanzwe kuri twebwe\tkuko udushikirije ubwo butumwa canke ntube mubabu dushikiriza"
  26,137,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari ingeso z’abantu baho hambere
  26,138,Natwe ntituzohanwa
  26,139,"Rero baramuhakana natwe duca tubibiza mumazi, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mu bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  26,140,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha hamwe n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,141,Bene Thamuda nabo nyene barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,142,"Mugihe mwene wabo yabwira intumwa y’Imana Swaleh (iii) ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya Imana yanyu"
  26,143,Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,144,"Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nanje mungamburukire"
  26,145,"Kandi nanje sindabasaba impembo kuri ivyo, mugabo impembo yanje iri ku muremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,146,Mbega muzosigwa mumahoro muri ibi bintu biri ngaha iwanyu
  26,147,Mumirima hamwe no mumasoko y’amazi
  26,148,N’ibiterwa vy’imitende bifise ivyamwa vyiza
  26,149,Mukabaza n’imisozi nukuyigira mwo amazu yanyu y’ukwinezereza mwo gusa
  26,150,"Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nanje mungamburukire"
  26,151,Kandi ntimu gamburukire amategeko yabo bahakanyi b’Imana
  26,152,Nabagira ubwononyi gusa kuri iy’Isi mugabo ntibayigire neza
  26,153,"Nabo bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri wewe uri mubantu barozwe"
  26,154,"Wewe\tntanakimwe\turimwo\tahubwo\turi\tumuntu\tnkatwe,\trero nutuzanire ibitangaro niwaba uvugisha ukuri kwama"
  26,155,"Nawe abishura ati:- iyi nyana y’Ingamiya nibe ifise izamu\tryukunywa amazi, namwe mube mufise izamu ryanyu ryukuvoma k’umusi wageneweko"
  26,156,"Kandi ntimuyikoreko ngo muyigirire inabi\thanyuma ntimuze mufatwe n’ibihano vy’umusi w’imperuka"
  26,157,Mugabo abo bantu barayikereye iyo Ngamiya nukuba mumaganya
  26,158,"Rero ibihano birabafata, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo, mugabo benshi muribo ntibavyemera"
  26,159,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tnyene\tububasha\tn’impuhwe zihagije"
  26,160,Abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) nabone barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,161,"Mugihe yababwira mwene wabo na Lutwi (iii) ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya Imana yanyu"
  26,162,Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,163,"Rero ni mutinye Imana yanyu, nanje mu ngamburukire"
  26,164,"Kandi jewe sindabasaba impembo kuri ibi vyose, mugabo impembo yanje iri kumana w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,165,Mbega mwebwe murangura amabanga yabubatse n’abagabo nkamwe mubiremwa vy’imana
  26,166,"Mukareka\tabo\tUmuremyi\twanyu\tyabaremeye\tmubagore\tbanyu,\tmu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri mubantu mwarenze uburimbi"
  26,167,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- nutareka kutubuza wewe Lutwi (iii) ntankeka wewe uzoba uri mubantu bazokwirukanwa ngaha muri iki gisagara turimwo"
  26,168,"Nawe abishura ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndimu bantu banka cane ivyo bikorwa vyanyu bigaritse vy’umwanda"
  26,169,Muremyi wanje nundokore n’aba bantu banje kuri ibi bintu bariko baragira
  26,170,Natwe duca turamurokora n’abantu biwe bose
  26,171,Dukuyemwo umutamakazi yari mubicara inyuma y’abandi bose
  26,172,Hanyuma duca turabahonya b’abandi
  26,173,"Duca tubamanurira imvura y’isegenya mbi cane, nayo yari iyaba gabishijwe"
  26,174,"Ntankeka ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo, mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  26,175,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,176,N’abantu bo mukibira nabone barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,177,"Mugihe intumwa y’Imana Shuebu (iii) yababwira ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya Imana yanyu"
  26,178,Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,179,Nimutinye Imana yanyu kandi mu ngamburukire
  26,180,"Kandi sindabasaba impembo iyariyo yose, mugabo impembo yanje iri kumuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,181,Nimwuzuze igipimo neza mugabo ntimube mubantu bagabanya kuri ivyo bipimo
  26,182,Kandi mupime kuminzani y’ukuri
  26,183,"Kandi ntimuba gabanirize abantu kubintu vyabo, kandi ntimugendere kuri iy’Isi namwe muri mu bantu b’abononyi"
  26,184,Nimutinye uwabaremye hamwe n’ibiremwa vyabayeho vyose
  26,185,"Nabo bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri wewe uri mubantu barozwe"
  26,186,"Na wewe ntiwari bwabeho, mugabo uri mubantu nkatwe, mu vy’ukuri twebwe tukubona nkuko uri mu bantu b’ababeshi"
  26,187,"Rero\tnutumanurire\tibimanyu\tvy’amajuru\tniwaba\turi\tmubantu bavugisha ukuri"
  26,188,"Nawe abishura ati:- Umuremyi wanje niwe afise ubumenyi buhagije bw’ivyo muriko muragira"
  26,189,"Baramwihakanye baca bahura n’ibihano vy’umusi w’igitutu, ntankeka ivo vyari ibihano vy’umusi uhambaye"
  26,190,Mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  26,191,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tnyene\tububasha\tn’impuhwe zihagije"
  26,192,Ntankeka iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu nimanurwa ry’Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  26,193,Yamanuye ibi vyose nukunagura intahe y’ukuri kandi yizigigwa
  26,194,Hejuru y’umutima wawe kugira ngo ube mu bantu batuza
  26,195,Mururimi rw’icarabu rutomoye neza ruri k’umugaragaro
  26,196,N’ibi vyose biri mubitabu vy’aho hambere
  26,197,Mbega nticari ikimenyetso kuribo yuko ibi vyose muncabwenge zabene Israeri babizi
  26,198,Nk’iyo tumanurira kuri umwe muribo atari mubwoko bw’Abarabu
  26,199,"Agaca\tabasomera\tayo\tmajambo\tntibari\tkuba\tmubemera\tbimwe vy’ukuri"
  26,200,Uku rero niko twinjiza mumishaha y’abantu babi
  26,201,Nabo ntibazo kwemera kugeza aho bazobona ibihano bibabaza
  26,202,Rero bazoshikirwa n’ivyo bihano giturumbuka nabo batabizi
  26,203,"Bazovuga bati:- mbega twebwe tuzoronswa akanya"
  26,204,Mbega bahimiriza kubihano vyacu
  26,205,Ubibona gute nk’iyo twobanezereza nk’imyaka myinshi
  26,206,Hanyuma ivyo bihano bibashikire nkuko bavyemerewe
  26,207,Bizobamarira iki muvyo banezerejwe
  26,208,"Kandi ntitwahoneje igisagara icarico cose, n’uko hari abatuza abantu"
  26,209,N’icibutso mugabo ntitwari mubahemukiye imitima yacu
  26,210,Nayo mashetani ntiyamanutse n’iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu
  26,211,Kandi ntibiba kuribo kandi ntibabishoboye
  26,212,Ntankeka barazitiwe mukwumva
  26,213,Rero ntuze usabe iyindi Mana hamwe n’Imana y’ukuri kugira ngo ntuze ube mu bantu bazohanwa n’Imana
  26,214,Utuze abantu bawe muri kumwe nabo n’abari hafi yawe
  26,215,"Kandi\twunamike\tibaba\tryawe\tkuri\turya\tagukurikira\tmuri\tbarya bakwemeye"
  26,216,"Nibiyonkora wewe nuvuge uti:- jewe ndikure yivyo muriko muragira"
  26,217,Kandi wizere Umuremyi wawe gusa afise ububasha n’Impuhwe zihagije
  26,218,Kuko ariwe akubona aho uhagaze hose
  26,219,N’ihindagurika ryawe ryose hamwe n’abapfukama bose bashize imitwe yabo hasi
  26,220,Mu vy’kuri Imana niyo yumva kandi niyo nyene ubumenyi buhagije
  26,221,Mbega ndababwire mubo Amashetani yama amanukirako
  26,222,Amanukira k’umuntu mukuru wumwadukizi w’ikintu afise ibicumuro bininiya cane
  26,223,"Babashikiriza amajambo bumvise, mugabo benshi muribo n’ababeshi gusa"
  26,224,N’abategura amajambo y’ubuhizi bakurikiranwa n’abantu bazimiye
  26,225,Mbega ntubona yuko abo bantu bakikuza kumpande zose
  26,226,Nabo bakavuga yuko aribo bavuga ivyo badashobora gushira mungiro
  26,227,"Dukuyemwo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza nuguhayagiza Imana kenshi na kenshi nukwihorana mugihe bahemukiwe ivyabo, n’ubu vuba mu bantu bahemukira abandi bazomenya ihindagurika ry’ingene bazo hindagurika"
  27,1,"Twaa, Siiyn, (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa). Aya n’amajambo ari mugitabu c’Imana gitagatifu ca Qur’aani kandi n’igitabu cuzuye mwo ibintu vyose ngira kamaro kandi n’igitabu gisigura ibikenewe vyose biri mw’idini rya Isilaamu"
  27,2,Iyi Qur’aani n’uburongozi hamwe n’inkuru nziza ku bantu bayemera bimwe vy’ukuri
  27,3,Aribo bahagarika amasengesho nugutanga imperezwa zabo nabo bafise icizero c’umusi w’imperuka
  27,4,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe batemera uwo musi w’imperuka twebwe twarasharije ibikorwa vyabo, kuri ivyo baguma batayataya"
  27,5,Abo nibo bazoronka ibihano bibi cane kandi abo nyene mw’ijuru nibo bazoronka uruhombo runiniya cane
  27,6,Mu vy’ukuri ni wewe wigishwa iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu ivuye kuwufise ubuhizi n’ubumenyi buhagije
  27,7,"Igihe intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) yabwira umuryango wiwe ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nabonye umukomezwa, ubu vuba ndabazanira inkuru zawo canke ndabazanira igishirira cawo caka kugira ngo mwote kuri uwo mukomezwa"
  27,8,"Mugihe yawushikira yaciye ahamagarwa ati:- wewe arahezagiwe n’uwuri muri uwu muriro hamwe n’uwuri hambavu yawo, kandi haninahazwa Imana Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  27,9,Ewe Mussa (iii) mu vy’ukuri ni jewe Mana yawe mfise ubushobozi n’ubuhizi bukwiye
  27,10,"Nujugunye iyo nkoni yawe, mugihe yayibona igenda genda nk’inzoka yarahindukiye asubira inyuma yiruka atarindiriye, ewe Mussa (iii) ntutinye ntankeka iwanje ntibatinya imbere yanje intumwa z’Imana"
  27,11,"Mugabo uwahemukiye umutima wiwe hanyuma agaca akabisha ineza amaze kugira amabi, mbega jewe sije mfise ikigongwe n’Impuhwe zihagije"
  27,12,"Niwinjize ukuboko kwawe mumpuzu yawe, kuzoca gusohoka gufise ibara ryera atamwanda uriko, bikaba ari mubimenyetso icenda vyo kwa Fir’auni hamwe n’abantu biwe, mu vy’ukuri bari mubantu babi cane"
  27,13,"Mugihe bashikirwa n’ibimenyetso vyacu bigaragara, baciye bavuga bati:- ubu n’uburozi buri k’umugaragaro"
  27,14,Barayahakanye amajambo y’Imana matagatifu mugihe imitima yabo ivyemeza gutyo kubera ubuhemu bwabo n’ukwishima kwabo rero nuce uraba impera n’imperuka yabagira amabi
  27,15,"Ntankeka twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Suleimanu (iii) ubumenyi baca bavuga bati:- ininahazwa ryose ni ry’Imana yaduteye iteka ntangere gusumba benshi mubiremwa vyiwe vyamwemeye"
  27,16,"N’intumwa y’Imana Suleimani (iii) niwe yatoranye ibisigi vy’intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) nukuvuga iti:- mwebwe bantu mwe! Twebwe twarigishijwe imvugo z’inyoni nuguhabwa ibintu vyose, mu vy’ukuri iyi n’ingabirano y’Imana iri k’umugaragaro"
  27,17,Yaregeranirijwe Intumwa y’Imana Suleimani (iii) ingabo ziwe z’ibisigo hamwe n’abantu n’inyoni nukuzitondesha imirwi n’iyindi
  27,18,"No mugihe bashika mumwaba w’ibikoko vy’ubunyegeri kimwe muri ivyo bikoko caravuze giti:- mwabunyegeri mwe! nimwinjire mumyobo yanyu intumwa y’Imana Suleimani (iii) ntibahonyange n’ingabo ziwe mugihe itabumva"
  27,19,"Nawe aramweyura atwenga kw’ijambo ryiwe nuguca avuga ati:- ewe Muremyi wanje, numpe ubushobozi nce ndagukengurukira kumihezagiro wampaye jewe hamwe n’abavyeyi banje, kandi mbashe kugira ibikorwa vyiza ushima kandi unyinjize mumpuhwe zawe mbe mu bantu bawe beranda"
  27,20,"Hanyuma aragenzura zanyoni ziwe nukuvuga ati:- vyakabaye gute ko ntabona yanuma, canke yabaye muyitari ngaha"
  27,21,Mu vy’ukuri ndayihana ibihano bikaze cane canke ndayibage canke inzanire ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro
  27,22,"Nawe ntiyamaze igihe kirekire cane aca avuga ati:- ndatahuye ico utotahuye kandi nje nturuka mugihugu ca Saba’a ndakuzaniye inkuru y’imvaho"
  27,23,"Mu vy’ukuri sanze Umupfasoni ategeka kandi yahawe ibintu vyose, kandi akaba afise n’inyegamo y’iteka iteye igomwe niniya cane"
  27,24,"Ndamusanze ari kumwe n’abantu biwe bapfukamira izuba aho gupfukamira Imana yabo y’ukuri, Shetani nayo ikaba yarabasharijije ibikorwa vyayo hamwe nukubazitirira inzira yabo y’amahoro, kuri ivyo rero abo bantu bose ntibarongotse"
  27,25,Nimupfukamire Imana ikura ibintu vyinyegeje biri mumajuru no kw’Isi kandi ikaba ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo munyegeza hamwe n’ivyo muserura
  27,26,Ntayindi Mana isengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa Umuremyi w’inyegamo yiwe ntagatifu
  27,27,"Intumwa y’Imana Suleimani (iii) ica ivuga iti:- tuzoraba yuko wavugishije ukuri canke uri mu bantu b’ababeshi"
  27,28,Nugende n’uru rwandiko rwanje uruba shikirize hanyuma ubareke uce uraba ivyo basubizanya
  27,29,"Wamwamikazi aca avuga ati:- mwebwe bategetsi, mu vy’ukuri nzaniwe urwandiko rw’iteka"
  27,30,"Ruvuye kuntumwa y’Imana Suleimani (iii) narwo ruvuga ruti:- Kw’izina ry’Imana nyene Imigisha myinshi, na nyene Imigisha mito mito"
  27,31,Ntimungirire ubwishime kandi muze iwanje namwe mwamaze kuba aba Isilamu
  27,32,"Wamwamikazi asubira kuvuga ati:- mwebwe bategetsi nimu mpanure kuri ibi vyipfuzo vyanje, kuko jewe sinshaka impanuro z’umuntu uwariwe wese kugeza aho mwese muba ivyabona"
  27,33,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- ni twebwe dufise ububasha hamwe nukurwana ingwano ikaze cane, n’itegeko riri iwawe rero nurabe ico utegeka"
  27,34,"Wamwamikazi aca avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri Abami iyo binjiye mubisagara vy’abantu baca bonona ivyo bisagara nukubagira bene ivyo bisagara kuba mu bantu barenganijwe, uko rero niko bama bagira"
  27,35,Mugabo jewe ndabarungikiye akaganuke hanyuma nanje nzorindira ico bazogarukana izo ntumwa zanje
  27,36,"Mugihe yashika kuntumwa y’Imana Suleimani (iii) yavuze ati:- mbega mwebwe mumfasha kumatungo? Uwayampaye nawe n’Imana nayo nimeza gusumba ivyo yahaye mwebwe, mugabo mwebwe munezerezwa n’izi nzimano zanyu"
  27,37,"Nimu bimusubize mu vy’ukuri tuzogenda n’ingabo zacu batazo shobora guhangana nazo kandi ntankeka tuzobakurayo bamaze gucika imvutu, kandi bamaze kudebukirwa"
  27,38,"Intumwa y’Imana Sulaymanu yarakoranije Abashikiranganji biwe bose avuga ati:- mwebwe bategetsi, ni nde ashobora kunzanira inyegamo yiwe y’iteka imbere yuko bashika iwanje nabo bamaze kuba aba Isilamu"
  27,39,"Umwe munkerebutsi z’ibisigo yavuze iti:- jewe nzoyigu shikiriza imbere yuku vyaguruka aho wicaye, nanje ntankeka ndafise ubushobozi bw’ivyo bintu kandi ndumwizigirwa"
  27,40,"Aca avuga umwe mubari bafise ubumenyi bw’igitabu ati:- jewe iyo nyegamo nzoyigu shikiriza imbere yuko urugohe rw’ijisho ryawe rutaranyiganga, rero mugihe yabona yanyegamo yiwe iri imbere yiwe yaciye avuga ati:- ibi vyabaye kubera ingabirano z’Umuremyi wanje kugira ngo angerageze arabe yuko no mushimira canke ndamu hakana, rero uwushima ashima kuneza y’umutima wiwe, nayo uwu hakana mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wanje niwe nyene amatungo n’umugizi w’ineza"
  27,41,"Aca avuga ati:- iyo nyegamo y’iteka nimuyihindure hanyuma turabe yuko ashobora kuyimenya canke azoba ari mubantu ataco bazi"
  27,42,"Mugihe yashika yabwiwe ati:- mbega iyi nyegamo yawe y’iteka yoba imeze nk’iyi? Nawe abishura ati:- egome inyegamo yanje yoba imeze nk’iyi nyene natwe tukaba twahawe ubumenyi imbere yukubona, mugabo natwe twari mu bantu b’abagamburutsi"
  27,43,Aca aramubuza nivyo yahora asenga biteye kubiri n’Imana; ntankeka yari mubantu b’abahakanyi imbere y’ico gihe
  27,44,"Ababwira ati:- nimwinjire munzu, mugihe yinjira yabajije yuko yinjiye mwidengeri ry’amazi, aca aduza impuzu ziwe kugeza kumavi, intumwa y’Imana Suleimani (iii) amubwira ati:- mu vy’ukuri iyo n’inzu yasakajwe n’ivyirori, nawe aca avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje narahemukiye umutima wanje none ubu nditanze hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Suleimani (iii) no kumuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  27,45,"Ntankeka twebwe twara barungikiye bene Thamuda (iii) hamwe na bene Swalehe (iii) tubabwira duti:- nimusenge Imana, munyuma yaho haciye habonekana imirwi ibiri yacanyemwo"
  27,46,"Aca avuga ati:- bantu banje, ni kuki muhimiriza kugira amabi imbere yukugira ineza? None ni kuki mutigera musaba ikigongwe kumana yanyu kugira ngo ikibagirire kumpuhwe zayo"
  27,47,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- twagize Imana mbi kubera wewe nukubera abari kumwe na wewe, nawe aca ababwira uti:- ukutumvikana kwanyu kuri kumana yanyu, mugabo kuri mwebwe muri mubantu Imana iriko iragerageza"
  27,48,"Muri ico gisagara harimwo abantu icenda bigize ba sura ivu mugukara cane kuri iy’Isi, kandi ata na kimwe bagize kubijanye n’uguhuza kw’abantu n’abandi"
  27,49,"Nabo bavuga bati:- nimurahire kumana yuko tuzotera intumwa y’Imana Swalehe (iii) mw’ijoro hamwe n’abantu biwe hanyuma tuze tumubwire uwuzo sigarana n’ibisigi vyiwe, natwe tuvuga duti:- twebwe ntitwabonye ihonywa ry’abantu biwe, ntankeka twebwe turi mu bantu bavugisha ukuri kuribo"
  27,50,"Baca bategura imigambi yabo, natwe dutegura iyacu, nabo batabizi"
  27,51,"N’urabe amaherezo y’imigambi yabo uko yari imeze, natwe rero twaciye tubahonya nabo bari kumwe bose"
  27,52,"Nizo nzu zabo zara garagara kubera ubuhemu bwabo, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo icigwa ku bantu bategera"
  27,53,Twaraba rokoye mubemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’abayi gamburukiye
  27,54,"N’intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) mugihe yabwira abantu biwe ati:- mbega muriko muragira ibintu vy’umwanda namwe mubibona"
  27,55,"Mukarangura amabanga yabubatse n’abagabo nkamwe kubera ivuduka ry’ivyipfuzo vyanyu bibi aho mwo biranguye n’abakenyezi banyu, mu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri mu bantu ata bwenge mufise. Igisomwa c’ubunyegeri.\tIkigabane ca"
  27,56,"Ntiyabaye inyishu y’abantu biwe atari uko bavuze bati:- nimu birukane abo bantu bakurikiye intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) mugisagara canyu kuko bari mubantu bisukuye"
  27,57,Twaciye tumurokora hamwe n’abamukurikiye dukuyemwo umutambukanyi wiwe duca tumushira murutonde rw’abantu bazokwicara inyuma y’abandi bose
  27,58,Duca tubamanurira imvura yari mbi cane nayo ikaba yari imeze gute! Yari yagenewe abantu batuzwa
  27,59,"Vuga uti :- ininahazwa ryiza ni ry’Imana n’amahoro ashikire intumwa ziwe yitoreye, mbega Imana niyo nziza canke bamwe bayi gereranya n’ibindi bintu"
  27,60,"Canke umwe yarema Amajuru n’Isi nukuba manurira amazi avuye mubicu no kuri ivyo twaranagishije imirima iteye igomwe, namwe ntabushobozi mufise bwukunagisha ibi biti, mbega hoba hari uwundi muremyi hamwe n’Imana rugira vyose, rero abo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri n’abantu batari kumurongo ugororotse"
  27,61,"Canke uwaremye iy’Isi ngo ibe ari ahantu hukuruhukira ho nugushira muriyo inzuzi n’imisozi, nugushira ho uruzitiro hagati y’ibiyaga bibiri, mbega hoba hari uwundi muremyi hamwe n’Imana rugira vyose, ahubwo benshi muribo ntana kimwe bazi"
  27,62,"Canke umwe yishura uwuri mungorane mugihe amusaba mukumukurira ingorane ziwe, nukuba gira ngo bagendesha iy’Isi, mbega hari uwundi muremyi hamwe n’Imana rugira vyose, nigakeyi cane kugira ngo mwebwe mutegere"
  27,63,"Canke umwe yabarongora mumwijima wo kw’Isi nugutwara imiyaga mugushikiriza inkuru nziza imbere y’imigisha yayo, mbega hoba hari uwundi muremyi hamwe n’Imana rugira vyose? Imana irisukuye hamwe nabayi gereranya nayo"
  27,64,"Canke uwatanguye kurema ibiremwa vyose hanyuma akazobigarura nkuko vyamye, nukubaha imigisha ivuye mw’ijuru no kw’Isi, mbega hoba hari uwundi muremyi hamwe n’Imana rugira vyose, nuvuge uti:- mwebwe nimuzane ivyemezo vyanyu nimwaba muvugisha ukuri kwama"
  27,65,"Vuga iti:- ntawuri mw’ijuru no kw’Isi afise ubumenyi bw’ibitariho atari Imana yonyene gusa nabone ntibazi ikihe gihe bazozurirwa ko"
  27,66,"Mbega bashikiwe ryari n’ubumenyi bwukumenya uwo musi w’imperuka, ahubwo nibo bafise amakenga y’uwo musi, ahubwo n’impumyi mukumenya uwo musi"
  27,67,"N’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bavuze bati:- mbega nitwaba twaramaze kuba ivu hamwe n’abavyeyi bacu, niho tuzozurwa"
  27,68,Ntankeka uku niko twemerewe hamwe n’abavyeyi bacu baho hambere bikaba bitari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari inyanduruko z’ububeshi z’abantu bakera
  27,69,"Vuga uti:- nimugende kw’Isi yose hanyuma mwitegereze ukugene vyabaye impera n’imperuka kuri ba bantu babi"
  27,70,"Kandi ntuterwe n’agahinda, kandi ntugire ibibazo kubera ingeso zabo bagira"
  27,71,"Kandi bavuga bati:- iyi ndagano izoboneka ryari nimwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  27,72,"Vuga uti:- nkumbure iri hafi yukubashikira kuvyo mwihutira kugira ngo bibe"
  27,73,"Kandi ntankeka Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene imigisha ku bantu bayo, mugabo benshi muribo ntiba shima"
  27,74,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe afise ubumenyi bw’ivyo munyegeza mubikiriza vyanyu hamwe nivyo muserura
  27,75,"Kandi\tntamabanga\tari\thagati\ty’Amajuru\tn’Isi\tatari\tuko\tari\thagati y’igitabu c’Imana kigaragaza ibintu vyose"
  27,76,Ntankeka iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu irabavuga bene Israeri kubintu vyinshi bijanye nukutumvikana kwabo
  27,77,Mu vy’ukuri iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu n’indongozi n’imigisha ku bantu bayemera
  27,78,"Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe azobacira urubanza rw’amategeko yayo, nayo niyo nyene inguvu n’ubumenyi buhagije"
  27,79,Rero niwizere Imana yawe mu vy’ukuri wewe uri hejuru y’ukuri kuri k’umugaragaro
  27,80,Mu vy’ukuri wewe ntushobora kwumvisha abapfuye ubwo butumwa bwawe canke kwumvisha abatumva mugihe bahindukiye bigira iyo baja
  27,81,"Kandi ntushobora kurongora impumyi ziri mubuzimire bwazo, kandi ntushobora kubumvisha atari abemera amajambo yacu y’Imana, abo rero nibo bagamburutsi"
  27,82,N’imvugo mugihe izoba shikira tuzoba kurira igikoko ngaha kw’Isi kizoba vugisha abo bantu kubera yuko batemera amajambo yacu
  27,83,"N’umusi tuzo kwegeranya mumirwi y’abantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, nabone bazoshigwa mumirwi nk’abandi"
  27,84,"N’igihe bazoshika Imana izovumera iti:- mbega mwebwe mwarahakanye amajambo yanje mutabizi neza, canke mwamye mugira iki"
  27,85,"Ijambo ry’ukuri rizobashikira kubera yuko bahemutse, rero ntaco bazovuga"
  27,86,"Mbega ntibabona yuko twaremye Ijoro kugira ngo abantu baruhukire mwo hamwe n’umutaga w’umuco, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso kubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  27,87,"N’umusi hazovuzwa inzamba hanyuma abari mumajuru nabari kw’isi bose baze bate imitwe hirya no hino, dukuyemwo uwo Imana yashakiye ntate umutwe wiwe hirya no hino, na bose bazoyi shikira nabo bafise ibimaramare"
  27,88,"Uzobona imisozi ukibaza yuko ihumuye nayo iriko iragenda nk’ibicu, uko niko Imana ikora kuko yakoze ibintu vyose, ntankeka niyo ifise inkuru y’ivyo mugira vyose"
  27,89,"Abazozana ineza bazoronka ineza gusumba iyo, nuko kuburagizwa kw’uwo musi bazoba bari mumahoro nawo"
  27,90,"Nabazogira ububisha bwabo amaso yabo azotabwa mumuriro udahera, none ntimuhembwa atari kuvyo mwahora mugira"
  27,91,"Ntankeka nategetswe ngo nsenge Umuremyi w’iki gisagara, ariwe yagiteye iteka kandi ibintu vyose nivyiwe kandi nkaba nategetswe yuko noba mubantu babagamburutsi"
  27,92,"Kandi nsome iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu, nukuba ndi mubarongotse, nuwurongotse aba arongotse kubwiwe, nayo uwazimiye wewe nuvuge uti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndi mu bantu batuza abantu"
  27,93,"Kandi uvuge iti:- ihayagizwa ryose ryiza ni ry’Imana kuko ubu vuba Imana izobereka ibimenyetso vyayo kandi muzobitahura, kandi umuremyi wawe ntiyibagira kuri ibi vyose mugira"
  28,1,"Twa, Siiyn, Miiym, (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  28,2,Aya n’amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ari mugitabu kiri k’umugaragaro
  28,3,Tugusomera inkuru y’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe n’inkuru ya Fir’aauni bimwe vy’ukuri kubera abantu bemera bimwe bivuye k’umutima
  28,4,"Mu vy’ukuri Fir’aauni yarigize akagarama ruganda kuri iy’Isi, hanyuma agira abantu bayo imirwi itandukanye n’iyindi, atako acinyiza umurwi umwe muribo mugukerera ibibondo vyabo vy’abahungu nugusiga ibibondo vy’abigeme bikirizi bizima, mu vy’ukuri uyo Fir’auni yari mu bantu b’abononyi"
  28,5,Hanyuma twashatse kubagirira impuhwe bamwe bacinyizwa kuri iyo Si nukubagira abategetsi nukubagira basamurarwa wayo mahirwe
  28,6,Nukubaha ingoga ngaha kw’Isi mukwereka Fir’auni hamwe na Hamana n’ingabo zabo kuvyo bahora batinya
  28,7,"Twaramweretse nyina w’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) yuko yokwonsa ikibondo ciwe no mugihe yoba amufitiye amakenga nace umushira mumwonga kandi ntatinye canke ngo agire agahinda, kuko twebwe tuzomugarura iwawe kandi tuzomugira mubazoba bari intumwa z’Imana"
  28,8,"Rero abantu bokwa Fir’auni nibo bamutoye kugira ngo abe umwansi hagati yabo n’agahinda, ntankeka Fir’auni na Hamana hamwe n’ingabo zabo bari mu bantu babi cane"
  28,9,"N’umukenyezi wa Fir’auni yavuze abwira Fir’auni ati:- ntumwice uyu azoba uwuzo nezereza amaso kuri jewe nawewe, kandi ntimumwice nkumbure azotugirira akandi kamaro, canke tumwitirire yuko ari ikibondo cacu mugihe nabo batabizi"
  28,10,N’umutima w’umuvyeyikazi w’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) usigara atakirimwo kuko yari hafi yugu serura amabanga iyo tudahumuriza umutima wiwe kugira ngo abe mubemera Imana yiwe y’ukuri
  28,11,"Abwira mushikiwe ati:- n’umukurikire, nawe aramwitegereza ari kure yabo nabo batabizi"
  28,12,"Duca tubuza abamwonsa kuva imbere y’igihe nawe avuga ati:- mbega ndabereke abantu binyuma bazomurera kubera mwebwe, kandi bazoba beza kuriwe"
  28,13,"Duca tumusubiza kwa nyina wiwe kugira ngo amaso yiwe anezerwe, kandi ntagire agahinda, kandi amenye yuko indagano y’Imana ari iy’ukuri mugabo benshi muribo ntavyo bazi"
  28,14,"N’igihe yashika mubigero vyiwe nugukomera twaramuhaye ubwenge n’ubumenyi, uko rero niko duhemba abagira ineza"
  28,15,"Yarinjiye mugisagara mugihe abasangwa biwe bari batabizi ahasanga abantu babiri bariko bararwana, umwe yari mubagenzi biwe, uwundi nawe yari mubansi biwe, rero wamugenzi wiwe yamusavye imfashanyo kubera wamwansi wiwe, intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) yaciye amukubita igipfunsi aho nyene aca aracikana, aca avuga ati:- iki n’igikorwa ca Shetani, ntankeka uyu n’umwansi atakaza ari k’umugaragaro"
  28,16,"Aca avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, ntankeka jewe nahemukiye umutima wanje rero nungirire ikigongwe, Imana nayo irakimugirira, mu vy’ukuri niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi hamwe n’impuhwe zihagije"
  28,17,"Avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje kubera yuko wampaye imigisha jewe sinzoba umufasha w’abantu babi"
  28,18,"Buramucako nawe ari mugisagara afise ubwoba arindiriye, mukanya wamuntu yasaba imfashanyo kuriwe ejo hahise amuhamagara ati:- ewe ntumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) nawe amubwira ati:- ntankeka wewe uri mu bantu bazimiye bari k’umugaragaro"
  28,19,"Mugihe yashaka kumufata mumaboko yiwe umwe yari umwansi wa bose uko bari babiri yaciye avuga ati:- ewe ntumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ugomba kunyica nkuko wishe umuntu ejo hahise, wewe ntakindi ugamije atari ukuba umuntu afise ubushobozi bw’iki gisagara kandi ntugomba yuko uba mu bantu bintore"
  28,20,"Haraje umuntu avuye inyuma y’igisagara yiruka cane aca avuga ati:- ewe ntumwa y’Imana Mussa abategetsi bakino gisagara bariko barumvikana yuko bokugandagura, rero nuve ngaha ntankeka jewe ndimu bantu bagushakira amahoro"
  28,21,"Aragenda afise ubwoba arindiriye ico mushikira avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, nundokore naba bantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  28,22,"Mugihe yatumbera mugisagara ca Madyana yavuze ati:- nkumbure Umuremyi wanje yondongora munzira y’ukuri"
  28,23,"Mugihe yashikira amazi y’ico gisagara ca Madyana yahasanze umurwi w’abantu banyweshereza ibitungwa vyabo, hanyuma kuruhande rwabo ahasanga abapfasoni babiri bazitiriwe, intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) aca avuga ati:- mufise ingone nyabaki? Baca bamwishura bati:- twebwe ntidushobora kunyweshereza intungwa zacu kugeza aho abo bungere bose bacura ibitungwa vyabo n’umuvyeyi wacu n’uwugeze muzabukuru"
  28,24,"Aca arazi banyweshereza za ntungwa hanyuma aca asubira mugitutu avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje ntankeka jewe ndi mubakeneye amahirwe uzomanurira kuneza nziza z’abakene"
  28,25,"Aca ashikirwa n’umwe muri babapfasoni babiri barajana nawe afise isoni, avuga ati:- Umuvyeyi wanje aragutumyeko kugira ngo aguhembe impembo yawe wakoreye yukutunyweshereza ibitungwa vyacu, rero mugihe yamushikira nuku mwiganira ivyabaye vyose, yavuze ati:- ntutinye uramaze kurokoka n’abantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  28,26,"Aca avuga umwe muri babapfasoni babiri ati:- ewe data wanje, numukoteshe uyu nyene, ntankeka umwiza ashoboye kukodeshwa nurya afise ubushobozi kandi yizigiwe"
  28,27,"Avuga ati:- jewe ngomba ndaguhe umwe muri aba bigeme banje babiri nuguca ingero y’imyaka umunani, niwakwiza imyaka cumi bizovana na wewe mugabo jewe sinshaka kukugora kuko uzonsanga Imana ibishatse ndimu bantu bagira ineza"
  28,28,"Avuga ati:- ivyo biraheze hagati yanje na wewe mugabo ikiringo nzomarira ko sinze mperanirwe, n’Imana niyo ikingira kuri ibi vyose tuvuga"
  28,29,"Ihihe yakwiza ikiringo ciwe intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) yaciye afata urugendo hamwe n’umuryango wiwe basubira iwabo iyo yavuye, aca abona umukomezwa uri kumpande y’umusozi, aca abwira umuryango wiwe ati:- nimu ndorerere ng’aha muvy’ukuri nabonye umukomezwa nkumbure ndabazanira inkuru zawo canke ndabazanire igishirira cuwo mukomezwa kugira ngo mwote"
  28,30,"Mugihe yashikira uwo mukomezwa kuruhande rw’iburyo ryuwo mwaba mukibanza cahezagiwe kivuye kugiti twaciye tumu hamagara duti:- ewe Mussa, ntankeka ni jewe nd’Imana, Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  28,31,"Nute iyo nkoni yawe hasi, rero mugihe yayibona inyiganga nk’inzoka yaciye ahindukira agenda adahindukira inyuma aca abwirwa ati:- ewe Mussa, nuze ngaha imbere mugabo ntutinye, mu vy’ukuri wewe uri mu bantu bari mumahoro"
  28,32,"Niwinjize ukuboko kwawe mundebuye yawe kuzoca gusohoka kwera derere atamwanda uriko, kandi wibangikanishe uko kuboko kwawe mugihe wiketse ikintu c’ubwoba, rero ibi bizoba ari ibimenyetso bibiri bivuye ku muremyi wawe kubera Fir’auni hamwe n’abakuru biwe, ntankeka abo n’abantu babononyi"
  28,33,"Yavuze ati:- Muremyi wanje, mu vy’ukuri jewe narishe umuntu muribo, kuri ivyo ntinya yuko bongandagura"
  28,34,"Namwene wanje Haruna (iii) niwe atomora amajambo neza gusumba jewe, rero numu rungike tube turi kumwe nawe abe umufasha wanje, mu vy’ukuri jewe ntinya yuko bazompakana"
  28,35,"Imana ica ivumera iti:- tuzoshiramwo ubushobozi kuri mwene wanyu kandi tuze tubahe intsinzi kugeza naho batazoba shikira kubera ibimenyetso vyacu kuri mwebwe hamwe nabazoba kurikira, muzoba mufise intsinzi nyakuri"
  28,36,"Mugihe Mussa (iii) yabashikira afise ibimenyetso biri k’umugaragaro baciye bavuga bati:- ibi bintu ntivyari kuba ibi mugabo ubu n’uburozi bwateguwe, kandi natwe ntitwigeze tuvyumva kubavyeyi bacu baho hambere"
  28,37,"N’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ica ivuga iti:- Muremyi wanje, urazi uwugushikiye n’uburongozi buvuye kuriwe, nuwuzoba afise amaherezo nukubaho kwiza, mu vy’ukuri aba hemukiye imitima yabo ntantsinzi bazoba bafise"
  28,38,"Nawe Fir’auni yavuze ati:- mwebwe bategetsi bakuru, sinabimenye kubera mwebwe iyindi Mana atari jewe gusa rero ewe Hamana nuncanire umukomezwa hejuru y’ivu, hanyuma uce unyubakira ikimenyetso kirekire kugira ngo mbashe kurunguruka Imana ya Mussa (iii), nanje ndamwikeka yuko ari mubantu b’ababeshi"
  28,39,"Yarishimye hamwe n’ingabo ziwe muri ico gisagara mugihe ata burenga nzira abufitiye, baca bikeka yuko batazo subizwa iwacu"
  28,40,"Natwe twaramuhanye hamwe n’ingabo ziwe, duca tubajugunyira mukiyaga, rero nimwitegereze ukugene amaherezo yabo bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  28,41,Twabagize abategetsi bahamagara abandi mu muriro udahera no k’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi ntibazo rokoka
  28,42,Tuba kurikizako umuvumo w’Imana kuri iy’Isi no k’umusi w’imperuka bazoba bari mubamerewe nabi cane
  28,43,"Ntankeka twahaye Mussa (iii) igitabu munyuma yuguhonya abantu baho hambere kugira ngo kibabere icuguruzo c’amaso y’abantu, kandi kibabere uburongozi n’imigisha kugira ngo bikebuke"
  28,44,"Kandi wewe ntiwari muruhande bw’uburengera zuba mugihe twamushira Mussa (iii) amategeko yacu, kandi ntiyari mubantu bari ngaho"
  28,45,"Mugabo twebwe twararemye abandi bantu benshi n’ubuzima bwabo kuba burebure kuribo, kandi wewe ntiwari umusangwa wakino gisagara ca Madyana wasomeramwo aya majambo y’Imana matagatifu, mugabo twebwe twahora turungika intumwa z’Imana gusa"
  28,46,Kandi ntiwari kuruhande rw’umusozi mugihe twamu hamagara mugabo n’imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe kugira ngo ubatuze abantu bada shikirwa nuwutuza imbere yawe nkumbure bazokwibuka
  28,47,"Kugira ngo ntimuze muhure n’ivyago kuvyo amaboko yabo yatanguje kugira baciye bavuga bati:- Muremyi wacu, mbega ni kuki uta turungikiye intumwa y’Imana natwe duce dukurikira aya majambo yawe nuguca tuba mu bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  28,48,"Mugabo mugihe bashikirwa n’ukuri kuvuye iwacu, baciye bavuga bati:- mbega ni kuki atahawe nkivyo yahawe Mussa (iii) mbega ntiba vyanse ivyo yahawe Mussa (iii) kuva kera nabo baca bavuga bati:- n’abarozi babiri bafashanya mu kuvuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri twese turabanka"
  28,49,"Vuga uti:- nimuzane igitabu kivuye ku Mana, murico harimwo uburongozi bwiza gusumba ibi bibiri kugira ngo ndamukurikire nimwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  28,50,"Nibatakwishura naho umenye yuko bakurikira muvyo bishakiye bonyene, none ni nde yazimiye gusumba urya arondera ivyo yipfuza ataburongozi buvuye ku Mana, mu vy’ukuri Imana ntirongora abantu bahemukira imitima yabo"
  28,51,Mu vy’ukuri twarabakurikije amajambo kugira ngo bibuke
  28,52,Abo twahaye igitabu imbere y’iki ariyo Qur’aani bamwe muribo baracemera
  28,53,"Mugihe basomewe aya majambo baca bavuga bati:- turayemeye kandi ntankeka uku niko kuri kuvuye ku Muremyi wacu mu vy’ukuri imbere y’ibi vyose twari mu bantu biyemeje imbere y’Imana"
  28,54,Abo bantu bazoronswa impembo zabo z’incuro zibiri kubera yuko bihanganye mugukura amabi kuneza nugutanga muvyo twabahaye
  28,55,"Mugihe bumvise ibihuha baca baja kure yabo nukuvuga bati:- twebwe dufise ibikorwa vyacu namwe mufise ivyanyu n’amahoro nabe kuri mwebwe, twebwe ntidushaka abantu b’ibijuju"
  28,56,Mu vy’ukuri wewe ntushobora kurongora uwo wishakiye mugabo Imana niyo irongora uwo yishakiye nayo niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’abarokoka
  28,57,"Abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri bavuze bati:- nitwakurikira ubwo burokoke turi kumwe nawe tuzoca dukurwa muri iki gisagara cacu, mbega ntitwabicaritse mungoro ntagatifu y’iteka y’amahoro iratirwa n’ivyamwa vy’ubwoko bwose, nukuba ari imigisha ivuye iwacu mugabo benshi muribo ntavyo bazi"
  28,58,"Twahoneje ibisagara bingahe vyigize akagarama ruganda kubera ubuzima bwabo, n’amazu yabo atabayabamwo munyuma yabo atari mu bantu bakeyi muribo, na twebwe nitwe basirwa babo"
  28,59,"N’umuremyi wawe ntahonya ibisagara ivyarivyo vyose kugeza aho arungika intumwa mugisagara cabo gikuru, hanyuma ibasomere amajambo yacu y’Imana, na twebwe ntiduhonya ivyo bisagara kugeza aho benevyo babaye abahemu"
  28,60,"Nicarico cose mwahawe mubikoresho vy’ubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi hamwe n’ibisharizo vyayo gusa, mugabo ibiri ku Mana nivyo vyiza nibizosigara, mbega ntimutegera"
  28,61,Mbega wamuntu twemerera indagano nziza kandi akazoyironka mbega azongana nuwo twahezagiye kumahirwe yo ng’aha kw’Isi gusa hanyuma k’umusi w’imperuka abe mubantu bazoshengezwa mu muriro udahera
  28,62,"N’umusi Imana izoba hamagara hanyuma ivuge iti:- bari hehe basomambike banje mwamye mwihayisha yuko turi kumwe nabo"
  28,63,"Bazovuga bamwe bashikiwe kuribo niyo mvugo bati:- Muremyi wacu aba bantu nibo twazimije, tubazimiza nkuko natwe twazimiye rero turabikuyeko imbere yawe kandi ntibasenga twebwe"
  28,64,"Hazovurwa hati:- nimuba hamagare basomambike banyu, mubisanzwe bazo hamagarwa mugabo ntibazobitaba ariko bazobona ibihano iyo bobaye mu bantu barongotse"
  28,65,"N’umusi Imana izoba hamagara hanyuma ize ivuge iti:- mbega mwishuye iki zantumwa z’Imana"
  28,66,"Inkuru z’uwo musi bazozibagira, nabo ntibazo shobora kubazanya icarico cose"
  28,67,"Nayo uwasavye ikigongwe nukwemera hamwe nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, nkumbure yoba ari mubazoba bafise intsinzi"
  28,68,"N’umuremyi wawe arema uko yishakiye akitorera uko yishakiye, abantu ntibanegura kuko iri kure nigabanukirwa ry’ibintu ivyarivyo vyose, kandi irisukuye nabo bayi gereranya n’ibindi bintu"
  28,69,N’umuremyi wawe arafise ubumenyi bw’ivyo ibikiriza vyabo binyegeza hamwe n’ivyo baserura
  28,70,"Nayo niyo Mana atayindi isengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene rudende, ihayagizwa ryose ryiza haba muntango canke kw’iherezo ryayo ryose nirwiwe, n’amategeko yayo yose n’amwe, mwese muzosubizwa iwe"
  28,71,"Vuga uti:- nimumbwire yuko Imana igize ir’ijoro ngo rigume ari ijoro gusa kugeza k’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi n’iyihe Mana atari Imana izoba garurira uwo muco? mbega mwebwe ntimwumva"
  28,72,"Vuga uti:- ni mumbwire yuko Imana igize umutaga ngo ugume ari umutaga gusa kugeza k’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi n’iyihe Mana atari Imana yonyene izoba garurira iryo joro? mbega mwebwe ntimubona"
  28,73,"Kubera impuhwe zayo, yarabagiriye Ijoro n’Umutaga kugira ngo muruhukire muri iryo joro nukurironderera mwo imigisha yaryo kugira ngo mushime"
  28,74,"N’umusi izoba hamagara nukuvumera iti:- bari hehe basomambike banje mwamye mwihayisha yuko turi kumwe nabo"
  28,75,"Tuzokura mu bantu babe ivyabona hanyuma tuze tubabwire duti:- nimuzane ibirego vyanyu, aho niho bazoca bamenya yuko ukuri kuri ku Mana kandi bazotakaza ivyo bahora badukana navyo"
  28,76,"Mu vy’ukuri Qaaruni yari mu bantu bo kuntumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) mugabo yarahemutse natwe twamuhaye ububiko bw’imfunguruzo zabwo zinanira gutwarwa n’abantu bafise inguvu abantu biwe bamubwiye bati:- ntiwishime mu vy’ukuri Imana ntikunda abantu bishima"
  28,77,"Kandi urondere kuvyo Imana yaguhaye bubwicaro bwiza bwo mw’Ijuru kandi ntiwibagire igice cawe c’ubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi, kandi ugire ineza nkuko Imana yabikugiriye, kandi nturondere kugira ubwononyi ng’aha kw’Isi, ntankeka Imana ntikunda abononyi"
  28,78,"Aca avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nahawe ibi vyose kubera ubumenyi mfise, ntiyamenye yuko Imana yahoneje imbere yiwe abantu bari bafise ubushobozi kumusumvya, kandi bari bafise umurwi muniniya w’abantu kandi babi batazobazwa ibicumuro vyabo"
  28,79,"Yaraserutse ku bantu biwe nkuko yama ashariza baca bavuga bamwe bipfuza ubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi bati:- iyo turonka nkuko yahawe Qaaruni, mu vy’ukuri niwe nyene imigisha mininiya"
  28,80,"Nabahawe ubumenyi bavuze bati:- oh! Impembo y’Imana niyo nziza kuwemera nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, kandi ntibazohabwa ivyo vyose atari mu bantu bihangana"
  28,81,"Twaciye duhonya uyo Qaaruni hamwe n’inzu yiwe mukuzimu, kandi ntawundi murwi wariho wukumufasha atari Imana yonyene gusa, kandi ntiyari mu bantu bashoboye kwifasha"
  28,82,"Bakaba bavuga bamwe bipfuza ubutegetsi bwiwe aho hahise bavuga bati:- ewe Mana ni wewe wongereza imigisha kuwo wishakiye ma bantu bawe, kandi ukima uwo wishakiye iyo Imana itatugirira impuhwe, ntankeka yari kuduhonya twese, mu vy’ukuri ntantsinzi y’abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri"
  28,83,"Iyo ngoro yo mw’ijuru tuzoyigirira bamwe badashaka kwishima kuri iy’Isi canke ubwononyi, n’impera nziza izokwegukira abantu beranda"
  28,84,"Uwuzogira ineza azoronka impembo nziza gusumba iyo neza yagize, nayo abazogira amabi ntibazo hembwa abo bagira amabi atari kuri y’amabi yabo bahora bagira"
  28,85,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo yagutegetse kugira ngo ukurikire iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu mu vy’ukuri izokugarura aho bagarukira, kandi nuvuge uti:- Umuremyi wanje niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’uwuzoza azananye n’uburongozi hamwe n’uwuzoba ari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  28,86,"Na wewe ntiwizera yuko uzoshikirizwa igitabu gitagatifu, mugabo n’imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe, rero ntube umufasha wabatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  28,87,"Kandi ntibakuzitire mugukurikira amajambo y’Imana matagatifu mugihe umaze kwugururirwa, kandi uhamagare abantu kumuremyi wawe kandi ntube uri mubantu bagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu"
  28,88,"Kandi ntusabe hamwe n’iyindi Mana, kuko atayindi Mana isengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa, rero ibintu vyose bizopfa dukuyemwo Imana yonyene rudende, icibwa ry’urubanza riri iwe, niwe niho muzo subizwayo mwese"
  29,1,"Alif, Laam, Miiym, (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  29,2,Mbega abantu biyumvira yuko bavuga yuko bemera bimwe vy’ukuri nabo ntibageragezwe
  29,3,"Oya! ntankeka twarabataye mungorane bamwe babayeho imbere yabo, mu vy’ukuri Imana izoba menyesha abavugisha ukuri, kandi izoba menyesha ababeshi"
  29,4,"Mbega biyumvira yuko bamwe bagira ivyaha yuko bazotunanira, imanza zabo mbi nizo zicibwa"
  29,5,"Uwushaka guhura n’Imana yiwe, mu vy’ukuri impanuka yayo izoshika atagisivya nayo niyo yumva, kandi niyo ifise ubumenyi buhagije"
  29,6,N’uwihangana ntankeka yihangana kubera umutima wiwe mu vy’ukuri Imana ntikeneye imfashanyo z’abantu
  29,7,N’abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe nukugira ibikorwa vyiza mu vy’ukuri tuzobagirira imbabazi kumabi yabo hanyuma tuze tubahembe kuvyo bahora bagira
  29,8,"Twarahanuye umuntu ngo agire ineza kubavyeyi biwe mugabo nibagutegeka ngo ugereranye Imana n’ibindi bintu nawe ata bumenyi ubifitiye ntuba gamburukire, kuko iwanje niho muzogarukira mwese hanyuma nzobabwira ivyo mwahora mugira vyose"
  29,9,Nayo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ukugira ibikorwa vyiza ntankeka tuzoba shira mu bantu beranda
  29,10,"No mu bantu bawe hari abavuga yuko bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri mugabo mugihe bashavujwe bari munzira y’Imana baca bagira amarorerwa ashikira abantu nkuko ari ibihano vy’Imana, rero habonetse amahoro avuye ku Muremyi wabo baca bavuga bati:- ntankeka twebwe twari kumwe namwe, mbega Imana ntabumenyi ifise bw’ukumenya ibiri mubikiriza vy’abantu bose"
  29,11,Mu vy’ukuri Imana izoba menyesha bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri kandi izoba menyesha ababeshi
  29,12,"Nayo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bavuze babwira abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bati:- ni mukurikire inzira yacu natwe tuzokwikorera ibicumuro vyanyu mugabo ntibazo shobora kwikorera ibicumuro vyabo n’ikintu na kimwe, mu vy’ukuri nibo babeshi gusa"
  29,13,"Mu vy’ukuri bazo kwikorera amatu yabo n’ayandi matu hamwe n’amatu yabo, mu vy’ukuri k’umusi w’imperuka bazobazwa kuvyo bahora barementanya"
  29,14,Ntankeka twararungitse intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) ku bantu biwe nukubana nabo kukiringo c’imyaka igihumbi ibura imyaka mirongo itanu mu nyuma yaho umwuzurire w’amazi warabashikiye mugihe bari mubahemukiye imitima yabo
  29,15,Twaramurokoye hamwe n’abantu biwe bari mubwato natwe duca tugira ngo kibe ari ikimenyetso kubantu bose
  29,16,"N’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) mugihe yabwira abantu biwe ati:- ni musenge Imana kandi muyitinye ayo niyo mahoro kuri mwebwe nimwaba mufise ubumenyi buhagije"
  29,17,"Mu vy’ukuri ni mwebwe musenga amasanamu nukureka gusenga Imana yanyu y’ukuri nukugira ububeshi, ntankeka barya musenga nukureka gusenga Imana y’ukuri, abo musenga ntabubasha bw’imigisha y’Imana bafise ahubwo ni musabe imigisha ku Mana kandi muyisenge nukuyishimira kuko iwe niho muzo subizwa yo"
  29,18,"Nimwa hakana mumenye yuko hamaze guhakanwa abantu baho hambere yanyu, kandi si kuntumwa y’Imana atari ugushikiriza ubutumwa bwiwe buri k’umugaragaro"
  29,19,"Mbega ntibabona ingene Imana yatanguye kurema ibiremwa vyayo, hanyuma ikazobigarura ubugira kabiri mu vy’ukuri ivyo vyose ku Mana n’ibintu vyoroshe cane"
  29,20,"Vuga uti:- nimugendagende kuri iy’Isi hanyuma mwitegereze ingene Imana yatanguye kurema, hanyuma Imana niyo izorema irindi shusho ryaho hanyuma, ntankeka rero Imana niyo nyene ububasha buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  29,21,"Imana ihana uwo yishakiye nukugirira ikigongwe kuwo yishakiye, kandi muzojanwa iwe mwese"
  29,22,"Namwe ntimushobora kuyinanira haba ngaha kw’Isi canke mw’Ijuru, namwe ntawubakingira mufise canke umufasha atari Imana yonyene gusa"
  29,23,"Na bamwe bahakana amajambo y’Imana matagatifu hamwe nuguhura nayo, abo bantu nibo bazokwihebura nukuronka imigisha yanje nabo nibo bazoronka ibihano bibabaza cane"
  29,24,"Rero ntiyabaye inyishu yabo bantu biwe atari uko bavuga bati:- nimumwice canke mumuturire, mugabo Imana yaciye imurokora nuwo muriro, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo icirwa ku bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  29,25,"Nawe yavuze ati:- mu vy’ukuri mwebwe mwagize amasanamu yanyu muyagira Imana aho kugira Imana y’ukuri hamwe nugukundana hagati yanyu mubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi, mugabo k’umusi w’imperuka mwese muzo kwankana muteko muvumane, hanyuma ubwicaro bwanyu buzoba ari ubwo mu muriro udahera kandi ntimuzoronka umufasha"
  29,26,"Rero intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) iramwemera nukuvuga iti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nimukiye ku Muremyi wanje, ntankeka niyo ifise ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  29,27,"Twaramuhaye intumwa y’Imana Is’haqa (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Yaaquubu (iii) hanyuma dushira muruvyaro rwiwe kuba ari intumwa y’Imana hamwe n’igitabu hanyuma tumuha impembo yiwe ng’aha kw’Isi, nawe k’umusi w’imperuka mu vy’ukuri azoba mubantu beranda"
  29,28,"N’intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) mugihe yabwira abantu biwe ati:- ntankeka mwebwe muriko muragira amabi kandi ata muntu n’umwe yabaye imbere yanyu yagize ayo mabi nkayo mu bantu bo ngaha kw’Isi"
  29,29,"Ni mwebwe muhuza ibitsina vyanyu muri abagabo kubandi nukuzitira inzira nukugira amabi mumanama yanyu, rero ntiyabaye inyishu y’abantu biwe atari uko bavuze bati:- nutuzanire ibihano vy’Imana niwaba uri mubantu bavugisha ukuri"
  29,30,"Yavuze ati:- Muremyi wanje, nunkingire n’aba bantu babononyi"
  29,31,"N’intumwa zacu mugihe zashikira intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) zimufitiye ubutumwa bwiza zaciye zivuga ziti:- ntankeka twebwe tuzohonya aba bantu b’iki gisagara, mu vy’ukuri aba bantu biwe babaye abahemu b’imitima yabo"
  29,32,"Avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri muri abo bantu harimwo intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii), nabo bavuga bati:- twebwe turabizi neza mubari muri ico gisagara, mu vykuri twebwe tuzomu rokora hamwe n’abiwe bose dukuye mwo umukenyezi wiwe azoba ari mubantu bazoba bicaye inyuma y’abandi"
  29,33,"N’intumwa zacu mugihe zashikira intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) yaramaramaye kubera abo bashitsi no kumutima wiwe waciye uba nabi kubera abo bashitsi bamushikiye, nabo baca bavuga bati:- ntugire ubwoba, kandi ntuteterwe ntankeka twebwe turakurokora wewe hamwe n’abantu bawe bose, dukuye mwo umutambukanyi wawe ari mu bantu bazoba bicaye inyuma y’abandi"
  29,34,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe tuzo manura hejuru y’abantu b’iki gisagara ibihano bivuye mw’Ijuru kubera ubuhakanyi bwabo
  29,35,Ntankeka twebwe twasize muri iki gisagara ibimenyetso biri k’umugaragaro kubantu bategera neza
  29,36,"N’abantu bokwa Madyana twarabarungikiye mwene wabo Shuweibu (iii) nawe avuga ati:- mwebwe bantu banje, nimu senge Imana kandi mutinye wa musi w’imperuka kandi ntimugende kw’Isi namwe muri abononyi"
  29,37,"Mugabo baramuhakanye, rica risokora imitima yabo nyamugigima, nabo bari munzu zabo baguye igihumure"
  29,38,"Nabene Aadi hamwe na Thamuda, no mumazu yabo twaraberetse neza ingene Shetani yabaryoheje mubikorwa vyabo bibi kandi bigaritse nukubazitira inzira mugihe bari mu bantu babona"
  29,39,"Na Qaaruni hamwe na Fir’auni na Haamana, mu vy’ukuri barashikiwe n’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ifise ibimenyetso biri k’umugaragaro mugabo n’abantu bishima kuri iy’Isi mugabo ntibashoboye gutsinda Imana"
  29,40,"Rero umwe wese twaramuhanye kubera ibicumuro vyiwe, hakaba muribo abo twashikirije igihuhusi c’umusenyi, n’abandi muribo basokowe imitima yabo kw’ijwi rininiya cane, n’abandi muribo twabatsindagiye mukuzimu, n’abandi muribo twabibije mumazi, rero ntiyari kuba Imana yoba hemukiye mugabo nibo bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  29,41,"Akarorero ni nk’abagize Imana atari Imana y’ukuri rero ni nk’akarorero k’igitangurirwa cishishira inzu yaco, ntankeka munzu ihoyahoye gusumba izindi nzu zose niyo y’igitangurirwa nkiyo bobimenya"
  29,42,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana irafise ubumenyi bwuko gusenga kwabo ibindi bintu nukureka gusenga Imana y’ukuri, nayo niyo ifise ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  29,43,"Nubwo burorero bwose nibwo twereka abantu, mugabo ntibategera atari mu bantu babizi"
  29,44,"Imana niyo yaremye Amajuru n’Isi bimwe vy’ukuri, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ivyemezo ku bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  29,45,"Nusome muvyo washikirijwe mubutumwa bw’Imana buri mugitabu c’Imana, hanyuma uhagarike amasengesho kuko ayo masengesho niyo akingira ibintu vy’umwanda n’amabi yose, mu vy’ukuri iyibuka ry’Imana niryo jambo rihambaye cane, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bwivyo mugira vyose"
  29,46,"Kandi ntimuharire n’abantu bahawe igitabu atari kubintu vyiza dukuyemwo abahemukiye imitima yabo muribo, kandi muvuge muti:- turemeye kuvyamanuwe kuri twebwe hamwe nivyamanuwe kuri mwebwe, n’Imana yacu hamwe n’Imana yanyu n’imwe, natwe n’abantu tugamburuka kuriyo"
  29,47,"Uku rero niko twakumanuriye iki gitabu, rero bamwe twaha iki gitabu baracemera no muribo harimwo abaracemera kandi ntibahakana aya majambo yacu atari babahakanyi b’Imana"
  29,48,"Kandi ntiwari mubasomyi bw’igitabu icarico cose imbere y’iki, kandi ntiwacanditse n’ukuboko kwawe kw’iburyo kuko bari kugira amakenga bamwe bagomba guhindura ukuri kwama"
  29,49,"Ahubwo aya n’amajambo ari k’umugaragaro kandi ari mubikiriza vy’abahawe ubumenyi, kandi ntibahakana amajambo yacu dukuyemwo abahemukiye imitima yabo"
  29,50,"Baravuze bati:- mbega ko tutamanuriwe ibitangaro bivuye ku Muremyi wiwe, wewe nuvuge uti:- ibitangaro vyose biri ku Mana yonyene gusa nanje mu vy’ukuri jewe ndimu bantu batuza kandi nshikiriza ubutumwa k’umugaragaro"
  29,51,"Mbega ntibahagijwe nuko twakumanuriye iki gitabu basomerwa, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo imigisha n’ubutumwa ku bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  29,52,"Vuga uti :- Imana yonyene irahagije kuba ari icabona hagati yanje na mwebwe, kuko niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mu Majuru no kw’Isi, na bamwe bemera ibitarivyo n’uguhakana Imana yabo y’ukuri, abo nibo bazoronka uruhombo"
  29,53,"Bagusaba ngo ubanyarukirize ibihano vyavuba na bwango mugabo iyo hataba umwanya wategekanijwe bari gushikirwa n’ivyo bihano, mu vy’ukuri ivyo bihano bizoba shikira giturumbuka mugihe bazoba batabizi"
  29,54,Baguhimiriza ibihano vy’Imana ngo bibashikire vuba na bwango mugihe umuriro udahera uzoba wabakikuje abo bantu batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  29,55,"Umusi bazofukwa n’ibihano bivuye hejuru yabo n’ibindi bizoba bivuye munsi y’amaguru yabo, nawe azovuga ati:- nimuhonje kuvyo mwahora mugira"
  29,56,"Emwe bantu banje mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, mu vy’ukuri iy’Isi yanje muriko iragutse cane, nanje nimunsenge gusa"
  29,57,"Umutima w’umwe umwe wese uzohonja urupfu, hanyuma muzo subizwa iwacu"
  29,58,"N’abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, ntankeka tuzobicarika mumazu agerekeranye kuyandi yo mw’ijuru hacamwo inzuzi imbere yabo, hanyuma baze babeyo mubuzima bwabo bwose, mbega n’imigisha imeze gute ku bantu bagira ineza"
  29,59,N’abihanganye nukwizera Umuremyi wabo
  29,60,"N’ibikoko bingahe bidashobora kwitungira imigisha yavyo, mugabo Imana niyo iha iyo migisha yayo hamwe namwe, kandi niyo yumva n’ubumenyi buhagije"
  29,61,"Ubajije abantu uti:- ni nde yaremye Amajuru n’Isi hamwe nukurema Izuba n’Ukwezi ntankeka bazo kwishura bati:- n’Imana, none bahindukizwa hehe"
  29,62,"Imana niyo iha imigisha yayo kuwo yishakiye mu bantu bayo, nukuyiha ibikwiranye nawe, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  29,63,"Ubabajije uti:- ni nde amanura amazi mubicu nukuzura Isi yari yarapfuye, ntankeka bazovuga bati:- n’Imana, nawe nuvuge uti:- ishimagizwa ryose rikwiriye Imana, mugabo benshi muribo ntavyo bazi namba"
  29,64,"Ntibwari kuba ubu buzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi atari uko ataco bumaze ari ugufyinata gusa, n’inzu yo mw’Ijuru aribwo buzima nyabwo nk’iyo bobimenya"
  29,65,"Mugihe buriye hejuru y’amato baca basaba Imana yabo y’ukuri, mugihe bayi ninahaza nukuyi gamburukira, mugabo Imana ibashikanye kw’Isi n’amahoro meza, baca bayi gereranya n’ibindi bintu"
  29,66,"Bashobore kuda shima kuvyo twabahaye kugira ngo binezereze, kumabi yabo mugabo ubu vuba bazobimenya"
  29,67,"Mbega ntibabona yuko twagize igisagara gitagatifu c’amahoro mugihe hasokorwa abantu bo kumpande zaco, mbega bemera ibitari ivy’ukuri nuguhakana imigisha y’Imana"
  29,68,"Ni nde muhemu mukuru gusumba urya abeshera Imana, canke uwuhakana ukuri kumushikiye, mbega simu muriro udahera ariho hazoba ubwicaro bwabo bahakanyi"
  29,69,"Nayo abihanganye kubera twebwe, mu vy’ukuri tuzoba yobora munzira zacu, kandi ntankeka Imana irikumwe n’abagira ineza"
  30,1,"Alif,\tLaam,\tMiiym,\t(Insiguro\ty’izi\tndome\thamwe\tnuwufise\tubumenyi bwazo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  30,2,Abarumi batsinzwe
  30,3,"Mugisagara kiri hafi yabo bamaze gutsindwa, mugabo bazotsinda"
  30,4,"Mumyaka mikeyi gusa itegeko ni ry’Imana yonyene imbere n’inyuma, y’uwo musi aba Isilamu bazonezerwa"
  30,5,"K’uburokoke bw’Imana irokora uwo yishakiye, nayo niyo ifise ubushobozi bukwiye n’impuhwe zihagije"
  30,6,Indagano y’Imana n’indagano Imana idatabwa mugabo abantu benshi ntavyo bazi
  30,7,"Barafise ubumenyi buboneka bujanye n’ubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’isi, mugabo bakihenda n’ubuzima bwo mw’ijuru budahera"
  30,8,"Mbega ntibiyumvira mumitima yabo yuko Imana itaremye Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibirimwo vyose yuko ari ivy’ukuri, no kugihe cagenywe mu vy’ukuri abantu benshi ntibavyemera yuko bazohura n’Umuremyi wabo"
  30,9,"Mbega ntibagenda genda kuri iy’Isi turiko nukuraba ukugene yabaye amaherezo y’aba bantu bamyeho imbere yabo, nabo bari bafise ubushobozi buhanitse kubasumba, bakaba barima kuri iy’Isi nuku yiringaniza neza kubasumba uko bahora bayi ringaniza, n’intumwa zabo z’Imana zarabashikiye zifise ibimenyetso biri k’umugaragaro, rero Imana ntiyari kubahemukira, mugabo nibo bonyene bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  30,10,Hanyuma impera yabagize amabi yose nuguhakana amajambo y’Imana matagatifu nukuyatyoza
  30,11,"Imana rugira vyose niyo yatanguje kurema ibiremwa vyose, kandi niyo izobigarura hanyuma bize bisubizwe iwe"
  30,12,"N’umusi umuhero w’Isi uzoshika, inkozi z’ibibi zose zizo debukirwa"
  30,13,"Ntibazoba bafise uwubasabira mubo bahora bagereranyako\tn’ibindi bintu, nabo bagereranywako n’ibindi bintu bazoba hakana icese"
  30,14,"N’umusi\tw’umuhero\tw’Isi\tuzoboneka\tkuri\tuwo\tmusi\tabantu bazocanamwo"
  30,15,"Nayo\tabemeye\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri\tnukugira\tibikorwa\tvyiza, bazonezerezwa nabo bari mumirima iteye igomwe iri mw’ijuru"
  30,16,"Nayo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, nuguhakana amajambo yacu hamwe n’ihuriro ry’umusi w’imperuka abo bantu bazoshengezwa n’ibihano vyo mumuriro udahera"
  30,17,Rero nimuyihayagize Imana mugihe c’ijoro hamwe no mugihe co mugitondo
  30,18,Nihayagizwa ryose ryiza niry’Imana haba mumajuru canke kw’Isi n’igihe co k’umuhingamo hamwe n’igihe co kumurango
  30,19,"Niyo ikura igifise ubuzima mukintu capfuye, nugukura ikintu capfuye mukintu gifise ubuzima, kandi niyo igira Isi kuba ari toto mugihe yari yarapfuye, rero uko niko muzozurwa"
  30,20,No mubimenyetso vyayo nuku kubarema ibakuye mw’ivu hanyuma nukuba abantu bakwiye
  30,21,"No mubimenyetso vyayo nuko yabaremeye abapfasoni banyu nkuko namwe mwaremwe kugira ngo muronke ihumurizo kuribo, nayo yabagiriye urukundo n’ikigongwe hagati yanyu, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso ku bantu biyumvira"
  30,22,"No mubimenyetso vyayo nukurema Amajuru n’Isi hamwe nugutahuza indimi zanyu n’amabara yanyu, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso ku bantu bafise ubumenyi buhagije"
  30,23,"No\tmubimenyetso\tvyayo\tnuko\tkuryama\tkwanyu\rkwo\rmw’Ijoro\rn’umutaga, n’ukurondera icorirenza, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi\rvyose\rharimwo\ribimenyetso kubantu bumva"
  30,24,"No mubimenyetso vyayo nukubereka imiravyo nukubatera ubwoba n’igihababu nukumanura amazi avuye mubicu, kuriyo igaca izura Isi yari yarapfuye, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso ku bantu bategera neza"
  30,25,"No mubimenyetso vyayo nuko Ijuru n’Isi bihagaze kw’itegeko ryayo, hanyuma mugihe izoba hamagara ihamagaro rimwe gusa mwese muzozuka mukuzimu"
  30,26,"Ibiri mumajuru no kw’Isi yose ni vy’Imana, kandi vyose nibi gamburukira Imana"
  30,27,"Nayo niyo yatanguje ibiremwa vyose ikaba nayo ariyo izobigarura bikaba kuriyo ari ibintu vyoroshe cane kuriyo, nayo niyo ifise ihayagizwa ryiza riri mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi nayo niyo nyene ububasha n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  30,28,"Yarabatangiye ko akarorero kubijanye n’imitima yanyu, mbega mubo mwitungiye n’amaboko yanyu y’iburyo harimwo abo mucuditse nabo muvyo twabahaye kugeza naho mungana nukubatinya nkuko mwitinyana kubwanyu, uku rero niko dutandukanya aya majambo yacu ku bantu bategera"
  30,29,"Mugabo abahemukiye imitima yabo nuko bakurikiye amatamariro y’imitima yabo nabo batabizi, none ni nde ashobora kurongora uwo Imana yataye mubuzimire, nabo ntibazoba bafise abazoba rokora"
  30,30,"Rero nutumbereze amaso yawe kw’idini ry’ukuri, kuko ariryo rema Imana yabaremeye abantu, rero ntahindagurika mwirema ry’ibiremwa vy’Imana, iryo niryo dini ry’ukuri mugabo abantu benshi ntavyo bazi"
  30,31,"Nimu gamburuke kuriyo kandi muyitinye kandi muhagarike amasengesho yanyu, mugabo ntimube muba gereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu"
  30,32,"Muba tandukanije idini ryabo nukuba imirwi n’iyindi, umurwi umwumwe wose unezerezwa nico ufise"
  30,33,"Abantu bashikiwe n’ivyago niho baca batabaza Umuremyi wabo n’ubugamburutsi ntangere, hanyuma iberetse imigisha yayo niho bamwe muribo baca bagereranya Imana yabo n’ibindi bintu"
  30,34,"Muguhakana muvyo twabahaye, rero nimunezerwe mugabo ubu vuba muzotahura"
  30,35,Mbega ntitwa bamanuriye ivyemezo bibakura amakenga kuvyerekeye uko kugereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu
  30,36,"No mugihe twabahonjesha abantu imigisha yacu baca bayihimbarira, mugabo mugihe bashikiwe n’ivyago kubera ivyo amaboko yabo yakoze, mumwanya isase baca badebukirwa"
  30,37,"Mbega ntibabona yuko Imana yugururira imigisha yayo myinshi kuwo yishakiye nukwima uwo yishakiye, ntankeka rero muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso ku bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  30,38,"Rero numuhe umubanyi ibikenewe kuriwe hamwe n’aboro nabari murugendo ivyo navyo ni vyiza kubashaka ikigongwe c’Imana, abo nibo bazoronka intsinzi nyakuri"
  30,39,"Nayo amahera mwatanze y’umurengero kugira ngo yongere kumatungo y’abantu mumenye yuko imbere y’Imana hatongereka ko n’ikintu nakimwe, mugabo muvyo mutanga kubera imperezwa nugushaka ikigongwe c’Imana rero abo bantu nibo bongerezwa inyungu kumatungo yabo"
  30,40,"Imana niyo yabaremye nukubaha imigisha yayo, hanyuma niyo izobica hanyuma ibazure, mbega muri bamwe mugereranya n’Imana yuko harimwo uwushobora kugira icarico cose muri ibi, rero itandukanye nuku gabanukirwa kukintu icarico cose kandi niyo iri hejuru gusumba kuvyo bayi gereranirizako"
  30,41,"Bwarabonetse ubwononyi ng’aha kw’Isi no mubiyaga kubera ivyakozwe n’amaboko y’abantu, rero kugira ngo ibahonjeshe bimwe mubintu bagize, nkumbure bogaruka"
  30,42,"Vuga uti :- nimugire urugendo kuri iy’Isi kandi mwitegereze ingene yabaye amaherezo yababaye imbere yabo, benshi muribo bari muba gereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu"
  30,43,"Rero nutumbereze amaso yawe munzira y’idini y’ukuri imbere yugushika kuri uwo musi utazitirwa uvuye ku Mana, kuri uwo musi niwo musi abantu bazo tandukanira"
  30,44,"Uwuhakanye uko guhakana kwiwe kuri hejuru yiwe wenyene, nabagira ineza bazigirira imitima yabo"
  30,45,"Kugira ngo ibahembe bamwe bemeye nukugira ibikorwa vyiza kumigisha yayo, ntankeka Imana ntikunda abahakanyi bayo"
  30,46,"No mubimenyetso vyayo nukuzana imiyaga ishikiriza inkuru nziza nukuba honjesha imigisha yayo, kandi kugira ngo amato agire hejuru y’ibiyaga kw’itegeko ryayo, nukurondera imigisha yayo nukuyi kengurukira"
  30,47,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twararungitse imbere yawe intumwa z’Imana ku bantu babo bakaba baje bafise ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro, munyuma yaho twaciye dubahana abagize amabi yose kandi vyari ngombwa kuri twebwe mukuba kingira abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  30,48,"Imana niyo izana imiyaga nukugendesha ibicu hanyuma ikabisanzaza mw’ijuru nkuko ibishaka, hanyuma ikabigira ibimanyu manyu ugaca ubona imvura irakorotse nugushika hasi nukuyishikana kubo yishakiye ku bantu bayo, nabo mumwanya ugaca ubabona banezerewe"
  30,49,Naho imbere yuku manurirwa iyo mvura bari bamaze kwihebura
  30,50,Rero nimurabe ibimenyetso vy’imigisha y’Imana ingene itotahaza Isi mugihe yari yarapfuye ntankeka Imana niyo izura abapfuye kandi niyo nyene ububasha hejuru y’ibintu vyose
  30,51,"Nkiyo tuzana umuyaga bakawubona ufise ibara ry’umuhondo, kuri ibi vyose bari kubandanya bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  30,52,"Na wewe ntankeka ntushobora kwumvisha ubutumwa bwawe ku bantu bamaze gushengera, canke ntushobora kwumvisha abatumva mugihe bahindukiye bigira iyo baja"
  30,53,"Kandi ntushobora kurongora impumyi ziri mubuzimire bwazo, kuko wewe ntiwumvisha abantu atari abemeye amajambo yacu, abo nibo bantu babagamburutsi nyabo"
  30,54,"Imana niyo yabaremye mubu goyagoye, no muyuma y’ubwo bugoyagoye ica ibaha inguvu, no munyuma yizo nguvu ica ibasubiza mubu goyagoye bwanyu hamwe n’ubusaza rero Imana irema uko yishakiye nayo niyo nyene ubumenyi n’ubushobozi buhagije"
  30,55,"N’umusi umuhero w’Isi uzohagarara, inkozi z’ikibi zizorahira yuko zitabaye kw’Isi atari isaha imwe gusa, uko rero niko bamye bahindaguzwa"
  30,56,"Nabahawe ubumenyi nukwemera bimwe bivuye kumutima bazovuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri mwebwe mubayeho kw’itegeko ry’Imana kugeza k’umusi wukuzurwa kwanyu, rero uwo musi nuwo kuzurwa mugabo mwebwe ntavyo mwari muzi namba"
  30,57,"Kuri uwo musi ntakizoba fasha ku bantu bahemukiye imitima yabo kubera ingorane zabo, kandi ntibazo kwemererwa ikigongwe cabo"
  30,58,"Mu vy’ukuri twaratanze akarorero k’ubwoko bwose kubera abantu muri iki gitabu c’Imana ca Qur’aani ntagatifu, mugabo ubashikirize ivyemezo ivyarivyo vyose, ntankeka abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bazovuga bati:- mwebwe ntimwari mu bantu bahindura ukuri aho kuri"
  30,59,Uko niko Imana itera igikumu kumitima yabamwe badategera
  30,60,Rero nurorere gusa ntankeka indagano y’Imana niy’ukuri kandi ntibagutere umutima uhagaze bamwe badafise icizero
  31,1,"Alif,\tLaam,\tMiiym.\t(Insiguro\ty’izi\tndome\thamwe\tnuwufise\tubumenyi bwazo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  31,2,Aya n’amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ari muriki gitabu categuwe neza cane
  31,3,Uburokoke hamwe n’imigisha niku bantu bagira ineza
  31,4,Bamwe bahagarika amasengesho yabo n’ugutanga imperezwa bakaba bafise icemezo c’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi yuko uriho
  31,5,"Abo nibo bari hejuru y’uburokoke buvuye ku Muremyi wabo, kandi nibo bafise intsinzi nyakuri"
  31,6,"Nomu bantu bawe harimwo abatora amajambo ataco amaze kugira ngo bahuvye abantu hamwe n’inzira y’Imana, nabo atabumenyi bw’ikintu na kimwe bazi, nugufyinata munzira y’Imana, rero abo bantu bazoronka ibihano bibatetereza"
  31,7,"Mugihe basomewe amajambo yacu matagatifu, baca bayaha imigongo mukwishima nkuko womengo ntibayumvise nkuko kandi mumatwi yabo harimwo uburemere, rero nubashikirize inkuru y’ibihano bibabaza cane"
  31,8,"Ntankeka bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, kuribo bazoba bafise imirima y’imigisha"
  31,9,"Bazobayo mubuzima bwabo bwose, n’indagano y’Imana ni y’ukuri, nayo niyo ifise ubushobozi hamwe n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  31,10,"Niyo yaremye amajuru yose atankingi zifise kandi arizo mwibonera, hanyuma ishiraho imisozi kuri iy’Isi kugirango ntibazingezinge nugukwiragiza ibikoko vy’ubwoko bwose nukumanura amazi avuye mubicu, no muriyo tunagishako ibiterwa vyiza vy’ubwoko bwose"
  31,11,"Ibi vyose Imana niyo yabiremye rero nimunyereke ivyahe baremye bamwe batari Imana, mugabo abahemukiye imitima yabo bari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  31,12,"Mu vy’ukuri twaramuhaye intumwa y’Imana Luq’manu (iii) ubuhizi duca tumubwira duti :- nukengurukire Imana yawe, n’uwuzo kenguruka muri mwebwe mu vy’ukuri azoba akengurukiye umutima wiwe, nayo uwuzoba ari umuhakanyi w’Imana y’ukuri, Imana niyo nyene ubutunzi kandi ihayagizwa hose"
  31,13,"Nawe Luqmanu mugihe yabwira ikibondo ciwe nawe ariko aramuhanura avuga ati:- mwananje ntuhirahire ngo ugereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu, kuko ukugereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu nibwo buhemu bukuru cane"
  31,14,Twarahanuye umuntu kubera abavyeyi biwe kuko nyina wiwe yasamye inda yiwe k’uburuhe n’ubundi nukumucusha kw’ibere kukiringo c’imyaka ibiri yuko yonshimira abavyeyi bawe kuko ingaruka yamwese n’iwanje
  31,15,"Nibagutegeka kugira ngo bangereranye n’ivyo ata bumenyi ufise, ntuba gamburukire, mugabo n’ubane nabo neza ng’aha kw’Isi, hanyuma ufate inzira yaba tumbera iwanje, hanyuma ingaruka yamwese n’iwanje, aho niho nzoba bwira muvyo mwahora mugira"
  31,16,"Mwananje, mu vy’ukuri ijambo iryariryo ryose rifise uburemere bwaryo nkubw’igishishwa c’imbuto y’icamwa c’umutende naho coba kiri hagati y’imisozi canke kiri mw’Ijuru canke kw’Isi, Imana izokizana ico kintu, ntankeka niyo nyene ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyinyegeje nibiri k’umugaragaro"
  31,17,"Mwananje, nuhagarike amasengesho yawe hanyuma utegeke abantu kugira ineza hamwe nugutuza amabi ayariyo yose, kandi wihangane hejuru yibizo gushikira, mu vy’ukuri ivyo nimu bintu bitegerezwa kugirwa"
  31,18,Kandi ntubarabire kuruhande rumwe rw’amaso kandi ntugire kuri iy’Isi n’ivyishimo vy’umurengera mu vy’ukuri Imana ntikunda uwo wese yishima nukwibona
  31,19,"Kandi ugire kurugendo rwo hagati na hagati kandi umanure ijwi ryawe, ntankeka ijwi ry’indogobwe niryojwi ribi cane gusumba amajwi yose mabi"
  31,20,"Mbega ntimubona yuko Imana yabaremeye ibiri mu Majuru no kw’Isi nukubakwiriza imihezagiro yayo iri k’umugaragaro n’iyindi iri mw’ibanga, hakaba hari abantu baharira kubijanye n’Imana atabumenyi bafise canke uburongozi bwavyo canke igitabu gifise umuco kurivyo"
  31,21,"Mugihe babwiwe bati :- nimu kurikire muvyo Imana yamanuye, nabo bishura bati :- ahubwo twebwe dukurikira muvyo twasanganye abavyeyi bacu bagira, mbega naho Sheteni ibahamagarira mubihano vyo mumuriro udahera harico"
  31,22,"N’uwushikanye amaso yiwe imbere y’Imana mugihe agira ineza, ntankeka azoba yamaze gufata ifundo rigumije neza, n’amaherezo y’ibintu vyose niku Mana yonyene gusa"
  31,23,"Nuwuhakana kuri ibi vyose wewe ntugire agahinda kubuhakanyi bwabo, ingaruka yabo n’iwacu, aho niho tuzobabwira ivyo bagize, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubumenyi bw’ibiri mubikiriza vyacu"
  31,24,Tuzoba nezereza gatoyi gusa hanyuma tuze tubasunike mubihano bigoye cane
  31,25,"Ubabajije uti:- ni nde yaremye Amajuru n’Isi ? Ntankeka bazo kwishura bati:- n’Imana, rero nimu babwire muti:- ishimagizwa ryose niry’Imana mugabo benshi muribo ntanakimwe bazi"
  31,26,"Ibiri mu Majuru yose no kw’Isi vyose nivy’Imana, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubutunzi nuguhayagizwa gukwiye"
  31,27,"Iyo ibiti vyose biri ngaha kw’Isi vyari kuba amakaramu, hamwe n’ibiyaga bifatanijwe n’ibindi biyaga indwi, aya majambo y’Imana ntiyari guhera, ntankeka n’Imana niyo ifise ubusobozi hamwe n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  31,28,"Ntikwari ukuremwa kwanyu canke ukuzurwa kwanyu atari nkuko ari umutima umwe gusa, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo yumva kandi niyo ibona"
  31,29,"Mbega ntubona yuko Imana yinjiza ijoro mumutaga nukwinjiza umutaga mw’ijoro, nuku gamburutsa Izuba n’Ukwezi ivyo vyose bigira kumwanya wageneweko, n’Imana niyo ifise inkuru yivyo mugira vyose"
  31,30,"Ibi vyose nukubera yuko Imana ari iy’ukuri nico basaba aho gusaba Imana yonyene ari ibitariho, n’Imana niyo nyene iteka rininiya cane"
  31,31,"Mbega ntubona yuko amato agendera hejuru y’Ibiyaga kumihezagiro y’Imana kugira ngo ibereke ibimenyetso vyayo, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso vy’umuntu yihanganye hamwe nuwushima"
  31,32,"N’imikuba ibahwikiye nk’ibicu baca batabaza Imana n’ubwitonzi ntangere, mugabo imaze kubarokora ikabashikana kunkengera z’ikiyaga muribo baca bafata urugendo ruri hagati na hagati rwiza nayo abandi barahakana imigisha y’Imana, kandi ntabahakana imigisha y’Imana atari uwoba yihenze mukuru ariwe muhakanyi karuhariwe"
  31,33,"Mwebwe bantu, nimu gamburukire Umuremyi wanyu kandi mutinye wamusi umuvyeyi atazofasha ikibondo ciwe, canke umwana ataco azofasha umuvyeyi wiwe n’ikintu nagitoyi, ntankeka isango ry’Imana niry’ukuri rero ntimugahendwe n’ubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi, canke ntimugahendwe n’urya mubeshi mukuru mubijanye n’ibintu vy’Imana"
  31,34,"Mu vy’ukuri ubumenyi bw’umuhero w’Isi buri ku Mana yonyene gusa, nayo niyo imanura imvura kandi ikaba ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri munda z’abakenyezi n’umutima uwariwo wose, kandi ntabumenyi ufise bw’ivyo uzogira ejo, canke umutima w’umuntu ntabumenyi ufise bw’aho azopfira, ntankeka Imana niyo nyene ubumenyi n’inkuru z’ibintu vyose"
  32,1,"Alif, Laam, Miiym. (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  32,2,Imanurwa ry’iki gitabu gitagatifu ntamakenga arimwo yuko kivuye k’Umuremyi w’abantu bose
  32,3,"Mbega bavuga yuko ariwe yaciyandikiye kubwiwe, ahubwo ico gitabu n’ukuri kuvuye k’Umuremyi wawe kugira ngo ugabishe abantu batashikiwe n’abagabisha imbere yawe nkumbure borongoka"
  32,4,"Imana niyo yaremye Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibiri murivyo mumisi itandatu, hanyuma yiganzira kunyegamo yayo ntagatifu, mwebwe aho muri ntawubacungera canke uwubasabira atariyo yonyene gusa, mbega mwebwe ntimwiyumvira"
  32,5,"Icisha ibintu vyose biri hagati y’Amajuru n’Isi, hanyuma hakaduga iwe k’umusi umwe gusa urugero rwavyo rw’imyaka igihumbi mukoresha mwebwe mugihe c’uguharura kwanyu"
  32,6,"Niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu bitazwi hamwe n’ibiri k’umugaragaro, kandi niyo ifise ubushobozi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  32,7,Ikaba ariyo yakoze ishusho ry’ibintu vyose nugutanguza irindi shusho ry’umuntu akoresheje ivyondo
  32,8,Hanyuma igira uruvyaro rwayo kw’ikanyuro ry’amazi ahoyahoye
  32,9,"Hanyuma iramu ringaniza nukumu huheramwo umutima wiwe nukuba shiriraho amatwi n’amaso n’imitima, mugabo ugushima kwanyu ni gutoyi cane"
  32,10,"Nabo bavuga bati:- mbega mugihe tuzoba twazimiye kuri iy’Isi niho tuzosubizwa murindi shusho rishasha, ahubwo nibo batemera yuko batazohura n’Umuremyi wabo"
  32,11,"Vuga uti:- Umumarayika ajejwe urupfu azobica kuko ariwe ajejwe kuri mwebwe, hanyuma mwese muzo subizwa ku Muremyi wanyu"
  32,12,"Iyo wobonye abo bantu babi bunamitse imitwe yabo imbere y’Umuremyi wabo bavuga bati:- Muremyi wacu turamaze kukubona nukukwumva, rero nudusubize kw’Isi kugira ngo dukore ibikorwa vyiza mu vy’ukuri turavyemeje"
  32,13,"Iyo dushaka twariguha umuntu uwariwe wese uburokoke bwiwe bwite, mugabo vyemejwe n’ijambo rivuye iwanje yuko mu vy’ukuri nzo kwuzuza mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu kuri aba bose haba mubisigo canke mu bantu"
  32,14,"Rero ni muhonje ibi bihano kubera ukwibagira kwanyu kw’uwu musi w’ihuriro ryanyu, natwe tuzobibagira nugu honja ibihano vy’urutavanako kubera ivyo mwahora mugira"
  32,15,Mu vy’ukuri abemera amajambo yacu nibarya mugihe bibukijwe kuriyo baca barwa hasi nugupfukama nuguhayagiza Umuremyi wabo nkuko imeze nabo bakaba batishima
  32,16,Bavyuka imbavu y’imibiri yabo mugihe bavuye mubusaswa bwabo mugihe c’ijoro kugira ngo basenge Imana yabo y’ukuri mugutinya umuriro nukwizera Ijuru ry’Imana gusa nugutanga imperezwa zabo kuvyo twabahaye
  32,17,"Umutima uwariwo wose ntabumenyi ufise bwivyanyegejwe murivyo binezereza amaso yabo, n’impembo yivyo bahora bagira"
  32,18,"Mbega umu Isilamu w’ijunja yoba angana n’umwononyi, oya! ntibashobora kungana"
  32,19,"Abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, bazoba bafise imirima hamwe n’ubwicaro bwabo bwiza, n’integuro ryabo kuvyo bahora bagira"
  32,20,"Nabamwe bagize ivyaha vy’agahomera bunwa, ubwicaro bwabo nubwo mumuriro udahera, kuko mugihe bashatse kuva muriwo bazoca bawu subizwamwo hanyuma babwirwe bati:- nimuhonje gusa ibihano vy’umuriro udahera mwahora muhakana"
  32,21,Mu vy’ukuri tuzoba honjesha ibihano bibayabaye imbere y’ibihano bininiya nkumbure bazo kwikubita agashi bakagaruka
  32,22,"None ni nde muhemu mukuru gusumba uwibukijwe kumajambo y’Umuremyi wiwe hanyuma agaca ayahakana, mu vy’ukuri twebwe tujejwe kugira ingere kuyindi kubantu babi gusa"
  32,23,"Ntankeka twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) igitabu, rero ntugire amakenga yuguhura n’Imana yawe, hanyuma tugira ico gitabu kuba ari indongozi kuri bene Israeri"
  32,24,Hanyuma tugira muribo kuba indongozi zukuyobora abandi bantu kw’itegeko ryacu mugihe bigumya bakaba bemeza amajambo yacu matagatifu
  32,25,Muvy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe azobacira urubanza rw’ukuri ruzoba hagati yabo k’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi kubijanye nivyo batahora bumvikana ko
  32,26,"Mbega ntibira menyekana kuribo yuko hari abantu bashika kuri bangahe twebwe twahoneje imbere yabo, nabo baca mumazu yabo, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso, mbega mwebwe ntimwumva"
  32,27,"Mbega ntibabona yuko twebwe dutwara amazi kw’Isi y’ubugaragwa hanyuma kuriyo tukanagishako ibiterwa biribwa n’ibikoko vyabo hamwe nabo bonyene, mbega mwebwe ntimubona"
  32,28,"Bavuga bati:- uko guciribwa urubanza ruzoba ryari nimwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  32,29,"Vuga uti:- umusi wuguciribwa urubanza rwabahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, ukwemera kwabo ntaco kuzobamarira kandi ntibazohabwa umwanya wukurorera"
  32,30,"Rero ntubiteho cane kandi urorere, mu vy’ukuri nabone bararindiriye"
  33,1,"Ewe ntumwa y’Imana, nubandanye utakambira Imana yawe y’ukuri kandi ntugamburukire abo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri hamwe n’ababeshi, ntankeka Imana niyo nyene ubumenyi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  33,2,Kandi ugume ukurikira muvyo washikirijwe mubutumwa buvuye k’Umuremyi wawe mu vy’ukuri Imana yawe niyo ifise inkuru zivyo mugira vyose
  33,3,Kandi wizere Imana yawe nayo niyo yihagije kuba ariyo ikingira ibintu vyose
  33,4,"Imana ntiyashize k’umuntu imitima ibiri mugikiriza ciwe, kandi ntiyagize abatambukanyi banyu mwatumbereje nabo imigongo yabo hamwe n’imigongo yabanyina banyu yuko banyina banyu, kandi ntiyagize ibibondo vyanyu vy’abazanano yuko bari mubibondo vyanyu kama, ayo n’amajambo yanyu yaturutse muminwa yanyu n’Imana niyo ivugisha ukuri kwama nayo niyo irongora inzira y’uburongozi bwiza"
  33,5,"Nimuba hamagare kumazina yabase wabo kuko ubwo nibwo buzoba buri mukuri imbere y’Imana, nimwaba mutazi abavyeyi babo, rero nibene wanyu muri mw’idini rimwe n’abagenzi banyu kandi ntamwikomo kuri mwebwe mugize amakosa nkayo mugabo kuri bimwe vyagizwe n’imitima yanyu kubigirampaka, n’Imana niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  33,6,"Intumwa y’Imana irafise uburenganzira gusumba aba Isilamu n’imitima yabo, n’abakenyezi nibo banyina babo nabo ni mubwoko bumwe kandi barafise uruhara rumwe nivyo musabikanya bimwe biri mugitabu c’Imana gusumba abandi ba Isilamu hamwe n’abahungutse mugabo nimwagira ineza kubagenzi banyu sibibi kandi ibi vyose biramaze kwandikwa mugitabu c’Imana"
  33,7,Mugihe twagira amasezerano kuntumwa z’Imana no kuri wewe nyene hamwe no kuntumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) no kuntumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) no kuntumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) no kuntumwa y’Imana Issa mwene Mariyamu (iii) abo bose twakiye indagano zikoma komeye kuribo
  33,8,"Kugira ngo ibaze abemeye kubijanye n’ukuri kwabo, kandi yaraba teguriye abo bahakanyi b’Imana ibihano bibabaza cane"
  33,9,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri nimwibuke imigisha y’Imana iri hejuru yanyu mugihe mwashikirwa n’ingabo natwe duca tubarungikira umuyaga hamwe n’ingabo zitaboneka, n’Imana niyo ibona ivyo mugira vyose"
  33,10,Mugihe mwashikirwa n’izo ngabo zivuye hejuru yanyu no hasi yanyu n’amaso yanyu azibonye imitima yanyu nayo ica iduga mumazosi yanyu namwe aho muri muca mutangura kwikeka ku Mana yanyu inyikeko zitandukanye
  33,11,Aho niho aba Isilamu batekerwa n’ibibazo nuku jugumizwa ijugumizo rikaze cane
  33,12,"No mugihe ababeshi b’Imana bavuga hamwe n’abarwaye mumitima yabo bati:- Imana hamwe n’Intumwa yiwe ntiba twemereye atari ububeshi gusa"
  33,13,"N’abantu bamwe muribo mugihe bavuga bati:- mwebwe basangwa bo ng’aha muri Yath’riba ntahandi hantu mwoba mufise hukubaho, rero nimusubire inyuma, uwundi murwi muribo waciye usaba uruhusha Intumwa y’Imana uvuga uti:- mu vy’ukuri inzu zacu ziragaragara mugabo ntizigaragara, mugabo ntaco bashaka atari uguhunga gusa"
  33,14,"Niyaba izo ngabo zarinjiye hejuru yabo muri ico gisagara kumpande zose z’igisagara hanyuma basabwa kugira ingwano gusa, bari kugira gutyo kandi ntibari kuguma muri ico gisagara atari mumwanya mutoyi gusa"
  33,15,"Mu vy’ukuri baramaze kugiriranira indagano n’Imana kuva kera yuko batazo hindura imigongo yabo inyuma, n’indagano y’Imana niyo kubarizwa ko"
  33,16,"Vuga uti:- uko kwiruka kwanyu ntaco kuzobafasha mwo nagatoyi, nimwaba muzohunga urupfu canke muzokwicwa, rero kuri ivyo ntimuzo ronswa umutekano atari mumwanya mutoyi gusa"
  33,17,"Vuga uti:- ni nde yoshobora kubakingira ku Mana niba mwoshikirwa n’inabi, canke ibashikira imigisha myiza, kandi ntibazoronka uwubakingira canke umufasha atari Imana yonyene gusa"
  33,18,"Ntankeka Imana irabazi bamwe bikingira muri mwebwe nababwira bene wabo bavuga bati:- nimuze iwacu nabo ntibagende kurugamba atari bakeyi cane"
  33,19,"Bazobagirira inzigo mugabo haje icobatera c’ubwoba uzoca ubabona bakwitegereza amaso yabo nayo ahindagurika hirya no hino nkuwaguye igihumure c’urupfu, mugabo ubwoba bubavuyemwo baca basubira kubashavuza kundimi zabo zikaze cane, bagaca bagira inzigo kumigisha y’Imana, abo rero ntibemeye kuri ivyo, Imana yaciye ibakurako imigisha y’ibikorwa vyabo, n’ivyo biroroshe cane ku Mana"
  33,20,"Biyumvira yuko yamirwi y’abansi babo itaragenda, iyaba iyo mirwi yogarutse bari kwipfuza yuko boba mubugaragwa hamwe n’abanya gihugu baho nyene babaza amakuru yanyu gusa, rero iyo mwoba muri kumwe namwe ntibari kurwana atari bakeyi cane muribo gusa"
  33,21,Ntankeka rero mwebwe muracafise akarorero keza kavuye kuntumwa y’Imana nukuwu tinya Imana yiwe hamwe n’umusi w’imperuka hamwe nugu takambira Imana cane
  33,22,"Naba Isilamu b’ukuri mugihe babona ingabo z’abansi b’Imana ziba shikiriye baciye bavuga bati:- ibi nivyo Imana yatwemereye hamwe n’intumwa yiwe, kuko bavugisha ukuri kwama, kandi nta n’ico batwongereje ko atari ibanga ryukwemera hamwe n’ubugamburutsi gusa"
  33,23,"Mu bantu harimwo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bakwijije amasezerano basezeranye n’Imana, muribo baramaze kurangiza ubuzima bwabo, n’abandi nabo baraca rindiriye, rero muri rusangi ntibigeze bahindura n’ikintu na kimwe"
  33,24,"Kugira ngo Imana ibarihe abanyakuri kubera ukuri kwabo nuguhana ababeshi ibishatse, canke ikabagirira ikigongwe, ntankeka Imana niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi cukugira ico kigongwe n’impuhwe nyinshi zihagije"
  33,25,"Naba hakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri yarabagaruye n’ishavu ryabo, hanyuma ntibaronka ineza iyariyo yose, hanyuma Imana ica irashigikira aba Isilamu mungwano zabo, nayo niyo nyene ubushobozi kandi niyo nziza"
  33,26,"Nayo yaciye ibamanurira bamwe bafashije mubantu bahawe igitabu kivuye mubirindiro vyabo hanyuma itera ubwoba mumitima yabo, bamwe muribo muca murabica n’abandi nabo muca mubagira imbohe"
  33,27,"Ica ibaha ibisigi vy’Isi vyabo hamwe n’amazu yabo n’amatungo yabo hamwe n’Isi mutari bwayihonyoreko, n’Imana niyo nyene ubushobozi buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  33,28,"Ewe ntumwa y’Imana, nubwire abo bakenyezi bawe uti:- nimwaba mukunda ubuzima bwo ngaha kw’Isi hamwe n’ibisharizo vyayo, nimuze ndabahe ivyoba nezereza n’ukwahukana kwiza"
  33,29,"Nimwaba mwipfuza Imana y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo hamwe n’inzu yo mw’ijuru, Imana yaraba teguriye abagira ineza muri mwebwe hamwe n’impembo niniya"
  33,30,"Mwabapfasoni b’intumwa y’Imana, uwuzogira ibicumuro ivyarivyo vyose muri mwebwe azo kwongerezwa ibihano kuriwe vy’incuro zibiri, n’ibi vyose n’ibintu vyoroshe imbere y’Imana"
  33,31,"No muri mwebwe uwuzo gamburukira Imana n’intumwa yayo hamwe nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, tuzomuha impembo yiwe y’incuro zibiri nukumu tegurira imigisha y’iteka"
  33,32,"Mwabapfasoni b’intumwa y’Imana, mwebwe ntimumeze nk’abandi bapfasoni basanzwe, nimwaba mushaka gutakambira Imana yanyu nukuyisenga, kandi ntimu hinyanyure amajwi yanyu kugira ngo ntaze agomwe n’umuntu arwaye mumutima wiwe, kandi muvuge amajambo meza"
  33,33,"Nimugume mumazu yanyu kandi ntimuze mwereke ibisharizo vyanyu k’umugaragaro nkuko bahora bereka abo bapfasoni mugihe c’ubujuju, rero muce muhagarika amasengesho yanyu nugutanga imperezwa, muteko mugamburukire Imana hamwe n’intumwa yayo, rero Imana igomba ibakurire umwanda mwebwe bantu bo munzu y’intumwa y’Imana, kandi igashaka yuko ibasukura neza cane"
  33,34,"Muba menyeshe ibisomwa biri mumazu yanyu no muri aya majambo y’Imana arimwo ubuhizi buhanitse, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu n’amabanga, kandi niyo nyene ubumenyi bw’ibintu biri k’umugaragaro"
  33,35,"Ntankeka abagabo bakurikirana neza inkingi z’idini rya Isilamu n’abakenyezi nuko nyene bazikurikirana, hamwe n’abagabo bemera neza bimwe bivuye kumitima yabo izo nkingi zukwemera nyakuri, n’abakenyezi bemera neza izo nkingi z’ukwemera nyakuri, hamwe n’abagabo bagamburuka, n’abakenyezi bagamburuka, hamwe n’abagabo bavugisha ukuri, n’abakenyezi bavugisha ukuri, hamwe n’abagabo bihangana, n’abakenyezi bihangana, hamwe n’abagabo bagamburuka, n’abakenyezi bagamburuka, hamwe n’abagabo batanga imperezwa zabo, n’abakenyezi batanga imperezwa zabo, hamwe n’abagabo bisonzesha, n’abakenyezi bisonzesha, hamwe n’abagabo bifata rupfasoni ntangere kubitsina vyabo, n’abapfasoni bifata rupfasoni ntangere kubitsina vyabo, hamwe n’abagabo bavuga Imana yabo y’ukuri umwanya wose, n’abapfasoni bavuga Imana yabo y’ukuri umwanya wose, abo nibo Imana yateguriye ikigongwe n’impembo niniya"
  33,36,"Ntibibaho k’umugabo yemeye Imana yiwe y’ukuri canke k’umukenyezi yemeye Imana yiwe y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yiwe mugihe baciriwe urubanza babe bafise aho bahengamiye kuri urwo rubanza rwabo, nuwu hakana Imana mu kwiyonkora ku Mana hamwe n’intumwa yiwe, mu vy’ukuri uyo muntu azoba yazimiye bimwe biri k’umugaragaro"
  33,37,"Igihe yabwira umwe Imana yahaye imigisha yiwe uca uramu hezagira, nufate umutambukanyi wawe kandi utinye Imana yawe, nukunyegeza ibiri kumutima wawe mugihe Imana yawe ariyo nyene ukuri nuguca utinya abantu aho gutinya Imana yawe y’ukuri mugihe uyo Zaidi yarangiza amabanga yiwe nkenerwa, nuyo mupfasoni niho twamuha uburenganzira bwukubakana nuyo mupfasoni kugira ngo ntihabe imyikeko n’ingorane kuba Isilamu mu kwubaka izabo n’abana babo b’abazanano mugihe bataba keneye, n’itegeko ry’Imana niryo ritegerezwa gukurikizwa gusa"
  33,38,"Ntamwikomo kuntumwa y’Imana kubintu Imana imaze kumu menyesha, bikaba ari ibisanzwe ku Mana ku bantu bahise baho hambere n’itegeko ry’Imana n’iteguro riteguwe neza"
  33,39,"Abahora bashikiriza ubutumwa bw’Imana hamwe nukuyitinya, rero ntanuwo batinya atari Imana, n’Imana niyo ihagije muguharura"
  33,40,"Intumwa y’Imana Muhammadi (aui) si umuvyeyi y’uwariwe wese muba shingantahe banyu, ahubwo n’intumwa y’Imana yanyuma muntumwa zayo zose, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  33,41,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ni mwibuke Imana yanyu kenshi na kenshi"
  33,42,Kandi muyihayagize iyo Mana kuva mugitondo no kumugoroba
  33,43,"Niyo ibaha iyo migisha hamwe n’Abamarayika biwe kugira ngo ibakure mumwijima nukuba shikana mumuco, kandi niyo iha imigisha yayo cane aba Isilamu"
  33,44,"Indamutso zabo zo k’umusi w’ihuriro n’Imana zizoba arindamutso z’amahoro, kandi yabateguriye impembo z’iteka ntangere"
  33,45,"Ewe ntumwa y’Imana, mu vy’ukuri twebwe twakurungitse ngo utubere icabona cugutanga inkuru nziza nukuba mu bantu batuza"
  33,46,"Kandi ube mu bantu bararika abandi kubera Imana, kandi kw’itegeko ryiwe, kandi ube uri urumuri rutanga umuco"
  33,47,Kandi ubahe aba Isilamu inkuru nziza yuko bafise akarusho kaniniya kavuye ku Mana yabo
  33,48,"Ntugamburukire abo bahakanyi b’Imana hamwe nabo babeshi, kandi ntiwiteho kumabi yabo, mugabo ugume wizera Imana yawe gusa, kuko ariyo ihagije mukugu kingira"
  33,49,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ni mwubakane n’abakenyezi bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri hanyuma ni mwahukana nabo batambukanyi banyu imbere yuguhuza nabo ibitsina, ntavyicaro bafise muzoba harurirako, mugabo nimubahe ico mwoba shumbusha kandi muze mwahukane nabo munzira nziza z’amahoro"
  33,50,"Ewe ntumwa y’Imana, twaraguhaye uburenganzira kubatambukanyi bawe wahaye agashimwe kabo hamwe nabo witungiye mukuboko kwawe kw’iburyo, wahawe n’Imana yawe hamwe n’abigeme babadata banyu batoyi, hamwe n’abigeme bayinasenge banyu, n’abigeme bayinarume banyu, n’abigeme babashiki banyokwanyu mwimukanye nabo, hamwe n’umukenyezi wumu Isilamukazi yitanze kubwiwe imbere y’intumwa y’Imana, nkuko intumwa y’Imana nawe yagomba kwubakana nawe kandi berekuriwe kuriwe gusa bitarekuriwe kubandi ba Isilamu, ntankeka twebwe turamaze kubimenyesha ivyo twabategetse kubakenyezi babo hamwe n’abakenyezi mwitungiye kumaboko yanyu y’iburyo kugira ngo ntihabe ingorane kuri wewe, n’Imana niyo nyene imbabazi nyinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  33,51,"Usubiza inyuma kuwo wishakiye muribo, nukwegereza hafi kuwo wishakiye, niwaba wamugomye uwo wamaze kwahukana nawe sibibi kuri wewe kugira gutyo kuzotuma unezereza amaso yabo aho kugumana agahinda kandi bashime wabahaye uko bari kwose, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mumitima yanyu, kandi niyo ifise ubumenyi, kandi niyo ntungane"
  33,52,"Munyuma yaba bapfasoni ufise ntabundi burenganzira ufise bwukubaka n’abandi bakenyezi canke kubahindura n’abandi bakenyezi naho ubwiza bwabo bwokunezereza dukuyemwo mubo wintungiye k’ukuboko kwawe kw’iburyo, n’Imana niyo irereka ibintu vyose"
  33,53,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ntimwinjire mumazu y’intumwa y’Imana kugeza aho muhabwa uruhusha rwukuja gufungura, nukutarindira kugeza aho ivyo bifungurwa bihira, mugabo ni mwaba mufise ubutumire aho niho murekuriwe kwinjira, kandi muhejeje gufungura nimuce mwitahira mutarinze gushinga ibiyago kuko ibintu nk’ivyo vyamye bishavuza intumwa y’Imana, nawe aho ari akagira isoni, mugabo Imana ntibona isoni ivugishije ukuri, namwe mugihe mubajije abapfasoni biwe nimubabarize inyuma y’uruzitiro, kugira gutyo n’ugusukura imitima yanyu hamwe n’imitima yabo, kandi sivyiza gushavuza intumwa y’Imana canke kwubakana n’abapfasoni biwe munyuma yiwe, rero kugira gutyo kizoba ari igicumuro kininiya cane imbere y’Imana"
  33,54,"Nimwa serura icarico cose canke mukaki nyegeza, ntimuzi yuko Imana ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  33,55,"Ntagicumuro kuribo no kuri badata babo, canke kubibondo vyabo, canke bene wabo, canke kubana babene babo, canke abana babashiki babo, canke abakenyezi nkabo, canke bamwe bitungiwe n’amaboko yabo y’iburyo, nimutinye Imana yanyu mwebwe bakenyezi kuko ntankeka Imana niyo cabona kiri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  33,56,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana imanura imigisha kuntumwa yayo hamwe no kuba marayika bayo, rero mwebwe aba Isilamu kandi muyisengere intumwa y’Imana muyisabira amahoro y’Imana n’imigisha nukumusabira amahoro"
  33,57,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bashavuza Imana hamwe n’intumwa yayo, abo bantu Imana yarabavumye kuri iy’Isi no mw’ijuru, kandi yaraba teguriye ibihano bibatetereza"
  33,58,"Nabarya bashavuza abagabo baba Isilamu hamwe n’abakenyezi babo ata n’ikosa narimwe bagize, ntankeka abo bantu nabikoreye ubuhemu buniniya hamwe n’ibicumuro biri k’umugaragaro"
  33,59,"Ewe ntumwa y’Imana, niwongorere abakenyezi bawe, hamwe n’abigeme bawe, hamwe n’abakenyezi baba Isilamu bamanure neza impuzu zabo, bagize gutyo bizotuma bamenyekana kugira ngo ntaba girirwe inabi, n’Imana niyo ifise imbabazi nyinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  33,60,"Niba abo babeshi hamwe nabafise ingwara mumitima yabo hamwe n’abiyamamaza kumabi yabo bari mugisagara, mu vy’ukuri twebwe tuzobigukura ko hejuru yabo hanyuma ntibazo kwicara ngaho hafi yawe atari mumwanya mugufiya gusa"
  33,61,Abo bantu baravumwe aho bari hose naho babonekera hose nibafatwe kandi bicwe
  33,62,"Ibi nibisanzwe kumana kuvyabayeho kubantu bamyeho kera, kandi ntuzoronka ihindagurika ry’ibintu bisanzwe ku Mana"
  33,63,"Abantu bakubaza inkuru z’umusi w’umuhero w’isi, wewe nuvuge uti:- ubwo bumenyi buri ku Mana yonyene gusa, none n’igiki kizo kumenyesha ko nkumbure umusi w’umuhero w’Isi uri hafi yugushika"
  33,64,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana yarabavumye abahakanyi bayo, kandi yaraba teguriye umuriro udahera"
  33,65,"Bazowuguma mwo mubuzima bwabo bwose, kandi ntibazo ronka umukunzi canke umufasha"
  33,66,"N’umusi waho mumaso yabo hazohinda gurirwa mumuriro udahera baze bavuge bati:- iyo tugamburukira Imana hamwe nuku gamburukira intumwa yiwe Muhammadi (aui)"
  33,67,"Bazovuga bati:- Muremyi wacu, mu vy’ukuri twebwe twakurikiye abategetsi bacu hamwe n’abakuru bacu, abo rero nibo batuzimije munzira y’ukuri"
  33,68,"Muremyi wacu, nubahe ibihano bimwe vy’akarorero abo bantu, vy’incuro zibiri zibiri, uteko ubavume umuvumo muniniya"
  33,69,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ntimube nkabagoye intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) mugabo Imana imugira mweranda kuvyo bamuvuzeko, nawe akaba yari afise urupfasoni ntangere imbere y’Imana"
  33,70,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nimuyitinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, kandi muvuge amajambo y’ukuri"
  33,71,"Izobagirira ibikorwa vyanyu vyiza, kandi izobagirira imbabazi kubicumuro vyanyu, nuwu gamburukira Imana hamwe n’intumwa yiwe, ntankeka uyo muntu azoba afise intsinzi niniya cane"
  33,72,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaraseruye amategeko yacu hamwe n’amatuzo yacu, kumajuru yose hamwe n’Isi n’Imisozi, vyose vyarahakanye kwakira ayo mategeko nukuyatinya, mugabo umuntu yarayakiye, ntankeka umuntu niwe muhemu mukuru, kandi atabwenge afise"
  33,73,"Kugira ngo Imana ihane abagabo b’ababeshi n’abakenyezi bababeshi hamwe n’abagabo bagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu, hamwe n’abakenyezi bagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu hanyuma ize igirire ikigongwe aba Isilamu b’abagabo n’abakenyezi, n’Imana niyo nyene ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  34,1,"Nidukengurukire Imana, kuko nivyiwe ibiri mu Majuru no kw’Isi no k’umusi w’imperuka ihayagizwa ryiza niryiwe, kandi niyo nyene ubuhizi n’ubumenyi buhagije"
  34,2,Niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyinjira kw’Isi hamwe nibiva muriyo hamwe n’ibishunguruka bivuye mw’Ijuru hamwe n’ibiduga muriyo nayo niyo nyene ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije
  34,3,"Abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri baravuze bati:- uwo musi w’umuhero w’Isi twebwe ntuzo dushikira, wewe nuvuge uti:- nukubera iki? K’ukuri k’Umuremyi wanje ntankeka uwo musi uzobashikira kuwufise ubumenyi bw’amabanga yose ntakizo kwinyegeza n’ikintu nakimwe naho coba gifise uburemere bw’akanyegeri kari mw’Ijuru canke kw’Isi canke ikintu gitoyi gisumba ico canke kininiya gusumba ico, nuko vyose biri mugitabu kibitomora neza kandi kiri k’umugaragaro"
  34,4,"Ize ibarihe bamwe bayemeye bimwe vy’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, abo bantu nibo bazoronswa ikigongwe n’imigisha y’iteka"
  34,5,"Nabihanganye muguhakana aya majambo yacu y’ukuri bagaca babona yuko bazodutsinda, abo bantu bazoronka ibihano bibi kandi bibabaza cane"
  34,6,Nabahawe ubumenyi barazi neza yuko ivyamanuwe kuri wewe bivuye kumuremyi wawe arivyo vy’ukuri nayo irongora munzira y’uwufise ubushobozi kandi ininahazwa hose
  34,7,"Nayo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bavuze bati:- mbega tubamenyeshe umuntu ababwira yuko mugihe muzota bagurwa mukaba ibimanyu manyu yuko muzoba muri murindi remwa rishasha"
  34,8,"Mbega yariyadukije n’ububeshi hejuru y’Imana canke n’umusazi, ahubwo abatemera umusi wimperuka nibo bazoba bari mubihano no mubuzimire bwakure cane"
  34,9,"Mbega ntibabona ibiri imbere yabo hamwe n’ibiri inyuma yabo biri mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi, rero iyo dushaka twari kubahonya kuri iy’Isi canke twari kumanura hejuru yabo ibimanyu vy’amajuru, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo itekerezo k’umuntu uwariwe wese yigaruye ku Muremyi wiwe"
  34,10,"Mu vy’ukuri twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) imigisha mininiya ivuye kuri twebwe tuvuga duti:- mwamisozi mwe, nimwitabire muri kumwe nawe mugu takambira hamwe n’inyoni zose, duca tumworohereza icuma"
  34,11,"Nuhingure inkinzo zagutse, kandi uzipime neza mukuzunga, kandi mugire n’ibikorwa vyiza, ntankeka ndabona ibikorwa vyanyu vyose mugira"
  34,12,"No kuntumwa y’Imana Suleimanu (iii) twaramu gamburukije umuyaga w’urugendo rwo mugitondo rwafata ukwezi kumwe n’urundi rugendo rwo kumugoroba narwone rwafata ukundi kwezi kumwe, duca tumu shuhiriza isoko ry’ubutare bw’umujumpu, no mubisigo vyagize ibikorwa imbere yiwe kw’itegeko ry’Umuremyi wiwe, nuwiyonkoye kw’itegeko ryacu muribo twaca tumu honjesha ibihano vy’umuriro waka cane"
  34,13,"Bahora bamugirira imirimo y’ivyo ashaka vyose haba munzitiro n’amasanamu hamwe n’ibirindi bininiya bingana nk’aho bakarabira hamwe n’amasufuriya maniniya cane adashoboka kuva aho yashizwe, rero nimukore mwa bantu b’intumwa y’Imana ya Daudi (iii) mugushimira imigisha Imana yabahaye, kandi nimu bantu bakeyi cane bashima mu bantu banje"
  34,14,"Mugihe yasandaba ntamuntu n’umwe yabamenyesheje kuri urwo rupfu rwiwe atari umuswa wariye inkoni yiwe, rero mugihe yarwa hasi niho ibisigo vyamenya yuko iyo bamenya ayo mabanga y’urwo rupfu rwiwe ntibari kwicarira muri ivyo bihano bitetereza gutyo"
  34,15,"Ntankeka ico cari icirwa ku bantu bokwa Saba’a mungo zabo no mumirima y’impande zibiri kuruhande rw’iburyo no kuruhande rw’ibubamfu, hose nimufungure kuri iyo migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu kandi muyi kengurukire n’iki gisagara ciza, n’Umuremyi wawe afise ikigongwe cinshi gihagije"
  34,16,"Mugabo ntibitayeho kumategeko y’Imana rero twaciye tuba shungurira ishunguriro rininiya ry’amazi ryatumye tubahindurira imirima yabo n’iyindi mirima ibiri harimwo ivyamwa bifise akanovera gakaze cane hamwe nayarura, n’ibindi navyo nka Ath’lin hamwe na Sid’rin n’ibindi"
  34,17,Uku niko twahaye indishi yabo kubera ubuhakanyi bwabo natwe ntitubahana atari k’umuntu yahakanye Imana yiwe y’ukuri
  34,18,"No hagati muribo hamwe no hagati y’ibisagara twahezagiye hamwe n’ibindi bisagara vyaboneka twashizemwo ibituro vy’ingenzi tubabwira duti:- nimubigendere ijoro n’umutaga muri mumwidegemvyo w’amahoro"
  34,19,"Mugabo bavuze bati:- Muremyi wacu, nutugirire urugendo rurerure ruri hagati y’ingendo zacu zose, nabo baca bahemukira imitima yabo ari naho twabacirako umugani nukuba shwiragiza kure nakure, mu vy’ukuri muri ivyo vyose harimwo icirwa ku bantu bigumya nugushimira Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  34,20,Ntankeka wamwansi w’abantu bose ariwe yitiriwe Ibilisi yaremeje amakenga yayo ari hejuru yabo nabo baca baramu kurikira dukuyemwo umurwi wabemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  34,21,"Nawe ntabubasha yari ifise kuribo mugabo kubera yuko twagomba kwerekana uwariwe muribo yemera umusi w’imperuka n’uwufise amakenga, n’Umuremyi wawe niwe aziganya ibintu vyose"
  34,22,"Vuga uti:- nimu hamagare abo babemerera izindi Mana atari Imana y’ukuri zidafise n’uburemere bw’agakoko gafise n’uburemere bungana n’akanyegeri koba kari mw’ijuru canke kw’Isi, kandi ntaho bacuditse muri ivyo vyose, kandi ntamufasha ifise muribo"
  34,23,"Kandi ntikuzo fasha ugusabirwa kwabo imbere y’Imana atari kuri wa muntu yahawe uruhusha kugeza naho hakurwamwo ubwoba buri mumitima yabo niho bazovuga bati: Umuremyi wacu yavuze iki? Nabo bazokwishura bati:- Yavumereye ukuri nayo niyo iri hejuru y’ibintu vyose kandi niyo nkuru"
  34,24,"Vuga uti:- ni nde abaha imigisha ivuye mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi ? Na wewe nubishure uti:- n’Imana yonyene, kandi ntankeka twebwe canke mwebwe, turi hejuru y’uburongozi canke turi mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  34,25,"Vuga uti:- mwebwe ntimuzo bazwa kubicumuro twebwe twagize kandi twebwe ntituzo bazwa kuvyo mwebwe mugira"
  34,26,"Vuga uti:- Umuremyi wacu niwe azo twegeranya twese hanyuma aze aducire urubanza rw’ukuri ruzoba hagati yacu nawe niwe mucamanza afise ubumenyi bukwiye"
  34,27,"Vuga uti:- nimunyereke uwabahujije n’Imana ngo mube mubafasha biwe, ivyo rero ntibishoboka mugabo niyo yonyene Mana ifise ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  34,28,"Ntitwakurungitse atari ku bantu bose, kandi ube umutanzi w’inkuru nziza hamwe n’uwutuza, mugabo abantu benshi ntavyo bazi"
  34,29,"Nabo bavuga bati:- niryari hazoba iri sango nimwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  34,30,"Vuga uti:- murafise isango ry’umusi mutazo cerezwa kuriryo sango n’isaha n’imwe canke mutazo yitanguriza imbere y’igihe cayo"
  34,31,"Baravuze b’abahakanyi b’Imana yabo y’ukuri bati:- twebwe ntituzo kwemera iyi Qur’aani namba canke ivyo bindi bitabu vyabayeho imbere y’ico gitabu, rero iyo wobabonye abo bahemukiye imitima yabo bahagaritswe imbere y’Umuremyi wabo nabo baterana imirarwe y’amajambo kuribo n’abandi, bamwe banyarucari bazobabwira bamwe bishima nukwibona mubakuru babo bati:- iyo hataba mwebwe ntankeka twari kuba aba Isilamu b’ukuri"
  34,32,"Bazovuga bamwe bishima mubakuru babo bababwira bamwe banyarucari bati:- yo! twebwe twarabazitiriye uburokoke munyuma yaho bwabashikira, ahubwo mwebwe nyene mwari mu bantu babi cane"
  34,33,"Nabamwe banyarucari bazovuga bababwira bamwe bishima aribo bakuru babo bati:- ahubwo amarorerwa mwagira y’ijoro n’umutaga mugihe mwadutegeka ngo duhakane Imana nukuyigira ngo tuyigirire abafasha bayo nabo bazonyegeza agahinda kabo bafise mugihe bazobona ibihano vyacu, natwe tuzoshira iminyororo mumazosi kuri bamwe bahakanye Umuremyi wabo w’ukuri, none hari ibindi bintu barihwa atari muvyo bahora bagira"
  34,34,"Rero natwe ntitwarungitse umuntu abatuza muri ivyo bisagara ivyarivyo vyose atari kubasangwa baho bifitiye uburyo bavuze bati:- ntankeka twebwe turiyamirije n’ibi mwarungikanywe navyo"
  34,35,"Nabo babishura bati:- twebwe turafise amatungo menshi hamwe n’ibibondo vyinshi kandi natwe ntituzohanwa"
  34,36,"Vuga uti:- mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wanje yama yugururira imigisha kuwo yishakiye nukwima kuwo yishakiye mugabo abantu benshi ntavyo bazi"
  34,37,"Si amatungo yanyu canke ibibondo vyanyu bizobegereza iwacu kurugero rwo mw’ijuru, ahubwo uwemeye Imana yiwe y’ukuri hamwe nukugira ibikorwa vyiza abo rero nibo bazoronswa impembo niniya cane kubera ibikorwa vyiza bakoze, nabo bazoba bari mumahoro ntangere kandi bari mumazu agerekeranye kuyandi ari mw’Ijuru"
  34,38,"Nabamwe bihangana muguhakana amajambo yacu bakabona yuko bazodutsinda, abo rero nibo bazoshengezwa mubihano"
  34,39,"Vuga uti- mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wanje yugururira imigisha yayo kuwo yishakiye ku bantu bayo kandi ikima kuwo yishakiye, n’icarico cose muzotanga niyo izobariha nayo niyo nyeranda yabatanga iyo migisha"
  34,40,"N’umusi Imana izo begeranya abantu bose hanyuma ize ibwire Abamarayika bayo iti:- mbega aba bantu bamye babasenga mwebwe"
  34,41,"Nabo bazokwishura bavuga bati:- uri kure n’ibida kwiranye na wewe, kandi ni wewe mukunzi wacu, sabo gusa ahubwo bamye basenga ibisigo na benshi muribo barabemeye"
  34,42,"Kuri uno musi benshi muribo ntibazo shobora bamwe muri mwebwe kubaha agahengwe bagenzi babo canke kuba kuriraho ingorane barimwo, kandi tuzobabwira bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo duti:- ni muhonje ibihano vyo mumuriro udahera mwamwye muhakana"
  34,43,"N’igihe basomewe aya majambo y’Imana matagatifu yacu ari k’umugaragaro baca bavuga bati:- ntiyari kuba uyo Muhammadi (aui) atari uko ari umuntu ashaka kuba kingira hamwe nivyo bahora basenga abavyeyi banyu, nabo bishura bati:- ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari ububeshi bwadutse giturumbuka, n’abahakanye Imana y’ukuri babwira ukuri kwabashikiye bati:- ibi vyose ntivyari kuba atari uko ari uburozi buri k’umugaragaro"
  34,44,Kandi ntitwa bahaye ibitabu ngo babisome kandi ntitwa barungikiye uwuba tuza imbere yawe
  34,45,"Barahakanye bamwe bamye imbere yabo kandi ntibara ronka ahantu hica cumi civyo twabahaye kuko baciye bahakana intumwa z’Imana zanje, rero ibihano vyanje vyari bimeze gute kuribo"
  34,46,"Vuga uti:- jewe ndiko ndabakebura kw’ijambo rimwe gusa, yuko mwohagarara bwuma kubera Imana muri babiri babiri canke umwe umwe hanyuma muce mwiyumvira muvuge muti:- uyu mwene wanyu si umusazi, rero ntiyari kuba atari uwuba tuza imbere yuko hashika ibihano bikaze cane"
  34,47,"Vuga uti:- impembo nabasavye nirwanyu mwebwe ntampembo yanje atari kumana yanje gusa nayo niyo cabona c’ibintu vyose"
  34,48,"Vuga uti:- ntankeka Umuremyi wanje niwe akwiragiza ukuri, akaba ariwe nyene ubumenyi bw’ivyo twebwe tutazi"
  34,49,"Vuga uti:- ukuri kwashitse, n’ikinyoma ntikizozana ikindi kintu gishasha, kandi ntikizo shobora gusubiza inguvu zaco"
  34,50,"Vuga uti:- ninaba narazimiye ntakundi, nzoba narazimiye kubera yuko nacumuriye umutima wanje wonyene, ninaba nara rongotse nukubera yuko nahawe ubutumire buvuye ku Mana, n’Umuremyi wanje ntankeka niwe yumva kandi niwe ari hafi"
  34,51,Wokwirabira ingene bahahamutse mugihe bazobona ibihano vy’Imana babe nk’abashaka kwiruka mugabo ntamahungiro azoba ahari kuko bazofatwa mumwanya mugufiya kandi hafi cane kandi barashika na kure
  34,52,"Nabo bazo vuga bati:- ubu rero turayemeye mugabo bazo shobora kuronka gute ubwo bw’Isilamu bari mukibanza ca kure"
  34,53,Mugihe bari bamaze kwidohora kuva kera kandi bakaba batitayeho kumajambo ataboneka avuye ku Mana nayo bayataye ahantu hakure
  34,54,"Hazoshirwaho uruzitiro ruzoba ruri hagati yabo no hagati y’ivyo bipfuza nkuko bagiriwe bagenzi babo baho hambere, ntankeka rero abo n’abantu bari bafise amakenga yatumye binubana kubera idini rya Isilamu"
  35,1,"Nidu kengurukire Imana Umuremyi w’Amajuru n’Isi, kandi ikaba ariyo yagize Abamarayika kuba arizo ntumwa zifise amababa abirabiri n’atatatatu hamwe n’anane, ikaba yongereza mukurema kwayo uko yishakiye, ntankeka Imana niyo nyene ubushobozi buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  35,2,"Imigisha Imana yugurura kubantu bayo, ntawushobora kuyikingira, kandi ntawu shobora kuyegeza imbere, nayo niyo nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  35,3,"Mwebwe bantu, nimwibuke imigisha y’Imana iri hejuru yanyu mbega hoba hari uwundi muremyi atari Imana yonyene gusa ibaha iyo migisha ivuye mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi, rero ntayindi Mana isengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa, none ni hehe muhindukizwa"
  35,4,Niba baguhakana umenye yuko bahakanye intumwa z’Imana imbere yawe n’ibintu vyose bizosubizwa kumana
  35,5,"Mwebwe bantu, ntankeka isango ry’Imana niry’ukuri, rero ntimuhendwe nubu buzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi canke wamubeshi mukuru yitiriwe Ibilisi ntabahende kubera Imana yanyu"
  35,6,"Mu vy’ukuri Shetani n’umwansi wanyu, namwe rero nimu mugire umwansi wanyu, kuko ihamagarira umurwi wayo kugira ngo ube ari uwo murwi wo mumuriro udahera"
  35,7,"Abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri hazoba kuribo ibihano bikaze cane, nayo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nu kugira ibikorwa vyiza, abo bantu nibo bazoronswa ikigongwe hamwe n’impembo itagira uko ingana"
  35,8,"Mbega umwe basharije ibikorwa vyiwe bibi, nawe akabibona yuko ari vyiza, ntankeka Imana yama ireka umuntu yishakiye akazimira, nukurongora uwo yishakiye, rero umutima wawe ntukuvemwo kubera agahinda kuribo, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo bagira vyose"
  35,9,"Imana niyo isunika imiyaga, ikana yinyarutsa hamwe n’ibicu ikabi shikana kw’Isi yapfuye, no kuriyo tugaca tunagisha iyosi mugihe yari yarapfuye, nivyaba ari uko niko kuzurwa kwanyu"
  35,10,"Uwushaka ubutegetsi, nuko ubwo butegetsi bwose ari ubw’Imana gusa, iwe niho haduga amajambo meza, n’igikorwa ciza nico kiduza amajambo amajambo meza gusa, nabamwe bagira ingeso z’amarorerwa mabi mabi, abo nibo bantu bazoronka ibihano bikaze cane, n’ingeso mbi zabo bantu zizohonywa"
  35,11,"N’Imana niyo yabaremye ibakuye mw’ivu, hanyuma kw’ima ry’intanga, hanyuma ibagirira abagabo n’abagore, n’umugore uwariwe wese ntashobora gusama imbanyi canke ntiyibaruka atari kubumenyi bw’Imana, nuwahawe ubuzima ntahabwa ubwo buzima bw’umurengero canke ntagaba nirizwa kuri ubwo buzima atari uko vyose biri mugitabu c’Imana gitagatifu, ntankeka ibi vyose biroroshe imbere y’Imana"
  35,12,"N’ibiyaga bibiri ntibimeze kumwe n’ikindi, kuko kimwe gifise amazi apfuse y’umusarara amanuka neza mumuhogo, n’ayandi nayo nay’umunyu abishe, no muri ivyo biyaga niho mufungura mwo inyama nshasha nugukura mwo ibisharizo mwambara, no muri ivyo biyaga mubonerayo amato asatura amazi kugira ngo muronkere mwo akamaro kayo kandi muteko muyishimire"
  35,13,"Niyo yinjiza ijoro mumutaga, nukwinjiza umutaga mw’Ijoro hanyuma igira Izuba n’Ukwezi, ivyo vyose bigenda ijoro n’umutaga kugeza k’umwanya wagenewe ushike, iyo niyo Mana, Umuremyi wanyu nyene ubwami, nabarya bayisenga ukutariko abo ntanico batunze nigishishwa c’urutete rw’umutende"
  35,14,"Nimwabasaba ntibumva akamo kanyu naho bokwumva ntiba shobora kubishura, no k’umusi w’imperuka bazohakana ubwo bugereranyi bwanyu bw’Imana y’ukuri, kandi ntibazo kubwira yuko bari hafi y’uwufise ubumenyi bw’ukuri"
  35,15,"Mwebwe bantu, ni mwebwe muri abakene kumana, nayo Imana niyo nyene ubutunzi kandi niyo ininahazwa hose"
  35,16,Ibishatse yoba kuraho mwese nukuzana ibindi biremwa bishasha
  35,17,Ibi vyose ntibigoye ku Mana
  35,18,"Ntawuzo kwikorera itu ry’uwundi muntu nuwoba yatakariwe n’iryo tu ryiwe, ahamagaye mugenziwe kubera iryo tu ryiwe, ntawuzo ryakira na gatoyi naho yoba ari mugenzi wiwe, mu vy’ukuri urabatuza kuri barya batinya Umuremyi wabo mugihe batamubona nugu hagarika amasengesho yabo, nuwisukuye yisukura kubera umutima wiwe n’ingaruka y’ibiremwa vyose ni ku Mana yonyene gusa"
  35,19,Ntibangana impumyi hamwe n’umuntu abona
  35,20,Canke umwijima hamwe n’umuco
  35,21,Canke igitutu n’ubushuhe
  35,22,"Kandi ntibangana abahema n’abapfuye, mu vy’ukuri Imana irumvisha uwo yishakiye, mugabo wewe ntushobora kwumvisha abari muntatemwa zabo"
  35,23,Ntiyari kuba wewe atari uko uri umutuza gusa
  35,24,"Ntankeka twebwe twakurungitse kubera ukuri kwama kugira ngo ubashikirize ubutumwa bw’Imana uteko ubatuze, kandi nt’abantu kw’Isi abaribo bose bataciyeko n’uwuba tuza"
  35,25,"Nibaguhakana naho, umenye yuko bahakanywe n’abari imbere yabo kuko bashikiwe n’intumwa zabo z’Imana bakaba nabo baje bafise ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro hamwe n’ibitabu vyukwandikira ko hamwe n’ibitabu birimwo umuco"
  35,26,"Hanyuma narabafashe bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri, rero ibihano vyanje vyari bimeze gute"
  35,27,"Mbega ntubona yuko Imana yamanuye amazi avuye mubicu, no kuriyo twakuyemwo ivyamwa bifise amabara atandukanye n’ayandi, no kumisozi harimwo n’imirongo yera niy’itukura ifise amabara atandukanye n’iyindi yirabura cane"
  35,28,"No mubantu hamwe no mubikoko harimwo murivyo vyamvura, n’ibindi bikoko bifise amabara atandukanye, mu vy’ukuri mubatinya Imana yabo bimwe vy’ukuri mu bantu biwe nibarya bafise ubumenyi, ntankeka rero Imana niyo nyene ubushobozi n’imbabazi zihagije"
  35,29,Mu vy’ukuri bamwe basoma igitabu c’Imana gitagatifu ca Qur’aani nugu hagarika amasengesho yose no muvyo twabahaye bagatanga mumwiherero no k’umugaragaro abo nibo bizeye ibidandazwa bidahomba
  35,30,"Kugira ngo ibahe impembo yabo ikwiye nukubongereza inyungu zayo, mu vy’ukuri niyo nyene ikigongwe nugu shimirwa"
  35,31,"N’igitabu twagu shikirije dukoresheje ubutumwa bw’Imana, nico gitabu c’ukuri cemeza ivyabaye imbere yiwe, ntankeka. Imana kubiremwa vyayo niyo ibazi kandi niyo ibabona"
  35,32,"Hanyuma twabasigiye ibisigi vy’iki gitabu gitagatifu ca Qur’aani mu bantu twatoye mu bantu bacu beranda rero muribo harimwo abahemukiye imitima yabo, n’abandi babayabaye, hakaba n’abandi bagenda imbere mukugira ibikorwa vyiza kw’itegeko ry’Imana, iyo rero niyo migisha mininiya"
  35,33,"Imirima y’ubudahera bazo kwinjira mwo, muriyo bazo sharizwa n’imigufu vy’inzahabu hamwe n’ibisharizo vyo mumazi bitiriye (ilulu), n’impuzu zabo zizoba zihwahutse cane"
  35,34,"Bazovuga bati:- ama ninahazwa yose meza na y’Imana yadukuyeko agahinda, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wacu niwe nyene ikigongwe cinshi na nyene gushimirwa"
  35,35,"Niyo yaturekuriye inyubakwa yukubamwo mubuzima bwacu bwose, muri iyo nzu ntavyago birimwo canke uburuhe"
  35,36,"Nayo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, bazoba bafise umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu, ntibazo ciribwa urubanza rw’ugupfa, kandi ntibazo gabanirizwa ivyo bihano, uku rero niko duhemba abadashima"
  35,37,"No muri uyo muriro udahera bazokoma yo induru muri uyo muriro udahera bavuga bati:- Muremyi wacu, dukure muri uyu muriro udahera tugire ibikorwa vyiza bitameze nk’ivyo twahora tugira tukiri kw’Isi, mbega ntitwabahaye ubuzima bw’ukwibuka uwibuka, nugushikirwa nuwutuza, rero nimuhonje ibihano mwebwe mwahemukiye imitima yanyu kuko mudafise uwuzoba rokora"
  35,38,Mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubumemyi bw’amabanga y’ibiri mu Majuru no kw’Isi ntankeka rero Imana niyo nyene ubumenyi bw’ibiri mubikiriza vyacu vyose
  35,39,"Imana niyo yabagize ngo mube ivyegera vy’abandi kuri iy’Isi, rero uko guhakana kwiwe kuri kugatwe kiwe n’ubuhakanyi bwabatemera Imana y’ukuri ntaco zibongereza imbere y’Umuremyi wabo atari ugushavurirwa gusa n’ubwo buhakanyi bw’abatemera Imana ntaco bubongereza atari uruhombo gusa"
  35,40,"Vuga uti:- mbega murabona abo mucuditse nabo aribo musenga aho gusenga Imana y’ukuri, rero nimu nyereke n’ahantu hatoyi h’Isi baremye canke boba bafise ishirahamwe mu Majuru canke twarabahaye igitabu no kurico bakaba bagifitiye ko ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro, mugabo abahemukiye imitima yabo ntibapfundika amasezerano yabo atari uko arimwo ibinyoma gusa"
  35,41,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ikingiye Amajuru n’Isi kugira ngo ntaveho, kuko avuyeho ntanumwe yoya kingira atariyo yonyene gusa, ntankeka rero Imana niyo ntungane n’ikigongwe cinshi gihagije"
  35,42,"Bararahiye ku Mana indahiro yabo niniya bavuga bati:- niba shikirwa n’uwubatuza ntankeka bazoba mubazo rongoka gusumba abandi bantu, mugabo mugihe bazoshikirwa n’uwuba tuza ntaco yobongereje atari uguhakana uko kuri gusa"
  35,43,"Kubera amanyama yabo kuri iy’Isi nukugira akajagari kabi kabi, nako kajagari kabi kabi ntikamanuka atari kuri beneko bakagize, none hari ikindi barorereye atari urutonde rwamyeho no ku bantu baho hambere, kandi ntuzoronka ihindagurika ry’urwo rutonde rusanzwe rw’Imana yagenye, canke ntuzosanga ihindagurika riri mubintu bisanzwe vy’Imana"
  35,44,"Mbega ntibagize urugendo kuri iy’Isi bakibonera impera n’imperuka yaba bayeho imbere yabo, kandi bakaba bari abantu bafise ubushobozi kubasumba, kandi ntakindi kintu gishobora kunanira Imana haba mw’Ijuru canke ng’aha kw’Isi, ntankeka rero Imana niyo ifise uburemyi n’ubushobozi bukwiye"
  35,45,"Iyo Imana ihana abantu kubera ivyo bakoze ntiyari gusiga n’umuntu numwe ngaha kuri iy’Isi canke n’igikoko na kimwe, mugabo Imana niyo iba rorereza kugeza k’umusi wagenywe, rero igihe c’umusi wabo kizoshika mu vy’ukuri Imana ku bantu bayo niyo ibabona"
  36,1,"Ya, Siiyn, (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  36,2,Ndarahiye kuri aya majambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’aani yateguwe neza cane
  36,3,Yuko mu vy’ukuri wewe uri muntumwa z’Imana
  36,4,Uri hejuru y’inzira igororotse
  36,5,Nimanurwa ryanyene ubushobozi n’impuhwe zihagije
  36,6,"Kugira ngo ubatuze abantu batatujijwe n’abavyeyi babo, rero nibo babaye abasamajwe"
  36,7,"Ntankeka n’ijambo ryemejwe kuri benshi muribo, kuri ivyo rero ntibavyemera"
  36,8,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twashize iminyororo kumazosi yabo kugeza kubusakanwa bwabo, rero imitwe yabo iraramye iri hejuru"
  36,9,"Twashize imbere yabo uruzitiro ruri imbere yabo n’urundi ruzitiro ruri inyuma yabo duca tubafuka mumaso yabo kuribo, kuri ivyo rero ntibabona na gatoyi"
  36,10,Nivyiza kuribo ubakebuye canke utabakebuye ntibazokwemera
  36,11,Woshobora kumutuza urya akurikira ubutumwa bw’Imana yamara kunyurwa nayo majambo y’Imana agaca atinya nyene imigisha naho atayibona rero numubwire uyo yuko ikigongwe hamwe n’impuhwe z’iteka ziri kuriwe
  36,12,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe tuzozura abapfuye kandi twandike ibikorwa vyabo bagira ntibize bisigare inyuma, n’ibintu vyose biri mububiko bw’igitabu cerekana ibintu vyose"
  36,13,Nubagirire akarorero k’abantu bo mugisagara kanaka mugihe bashikirwa naba shikiriza butumwa
  36,14,"Mugihe twabarungikira intumwa z’Imana zibiri barazi hakana natwe duca tubongereza inguvu tuba rungikira uwugira gatatu, bababwira bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe turungitswe kuri mwebwe"
  36,15,"Nabo babishura bati:- mwebwe ntaco murimwo, atari uko muri mu bantu nkatwe, nayo nyene imigisha ntanakimwe yamanuye, mwebwe muri ababeshi gusa"
  36,16,"Bavuze bati:- Umuremyi wacu niwe afise ubumenyi atamakenga arimwo yuko twebwe twarungitswe kuri mwebwe"
  36,17,Kandi ntakiri hejuru yacu atari ugushikana ubutumwa bw’Imana buri k’umugaragaro
  36,18,"Baca bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe ntitwumvikana kubera mwebwe nimutareka twebwe tuzoba tera iminana kandi izobashikira ivuye iwacu n’ibihano bibabaza cane"
  36,19,"Bavuze bati:- ukutumvikana kwanyu mwebwe nyene, yo! kuko mwibutswa mugabo mwebwe muri mu bantu mwarenze akarimbi"
  36,20,"Haciye haza umuntu ningoga na ningoga avuye kuruhande rwakure rw’ico gisagara avuga ati:- bantu banje nimukurikire izi ntumwa"
  36,21,"Nimu bakurikire babigishe batarinze kubasaba impembo iyariyo yose, mugihe abo bantu bari mubarongotse"
  36,22,"Nikuki ntosenga uwandemye, niwe ariho muzo subizwayo"
  36,23,"Mbega jewe nkurikire izindi Mana atari Imana yonyene rudende, niyaba Imana ishaka kungirira inabi, ibisabisho vyabo ntaco bizomarira n’ikintu na kimwe kandi ntibazondokora"
  36,24,Ninagira gutyo nzoba ndimu bantu bazimiye mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro
  36,25,Ntankeka jewe ndemeye Umuremyi wanyu mugabo ndabasavye mu nyumvirize
  36,26,"Ababwira ati:- niwinjire mw’Ijuru, nawe yishura ati:- iyo abantu banje babimenya"
  36,27,"Ingene Umuremyi wanje yangiriye ikigongwe nuku mpezagira, nkaba ndimu bahawe iteka ntangere"
  36,28,"Ntitwa bamanuriye abantu biwe arizo ngabo zivuye mw’ijuru, inyuma yiwe kandi ntitwari mubazi manura"
  36,29,"Ntacabaye atari akaruru kamwe nk’isase, bose baca bara zimangana"
  36,30,"Vyari\tkuba\tngombwa\tmukuba\thumuriza\tabo\tbantu\tbatashikiwe n’intumwa y’Imana n’imwe, mugabo bamye bijajurira gusa"
  36,31,Mbega ntibabona abantu isinzi twahoneje imbere yabo yuko batagaruka iwabo
  36,32,Kandi nta muntu uwariwe wese atazo shengezwa imbere yacu
  36,33,"N’ikimenyetso\tkiri\tkuribo\tn’Isi\tyapfuye,\ttuzoyizura\tnugukura\tmuriyo imbuto bazohora bafungura"
  36,34,"Tugira muriyo imirima hamwe n’ibiti vy’imitende n’imizabibu\thamwe nugu cishamwo amariba muriyo"
  36,35,"Kugira ngo bafungure muri ivyo vyamwa, kandi n’amaboko yabo ntaco yakoze, mbega ntibashima"
  36,36,Hahayagizwa Imana yaremye ikigabo n’ikigore muri vyose muvyo Isi inagisha no mumitima yabo hamwe nivyo batazi
  36,37,"N’ijoro\tn’ikimenyetso\tkuribo\tkuko\tariho\tbakura\tmwo\tumurango, mumwanya bagaca baba mumwijima"
  36,38,"N’izuba\trigenda\tgushika\tkugituro\tcaryo,\tiryo\tn’iteguro\try’uwufise ububasha n’ubumenyi"
  36,39,"N’ukwezi\ttwagupimiye\tibituro\tvyakwo\tkugeza\tnaho\tgusubira\tkuba gutoyi cane nk’igishishwa c’icamwa c’umutende gishaje cane"
  36,40,"Ntazuba rishikira\tUkwezi canke Ijoro ngo rirenge Umutaga, mugabo vyose biguma birerembera munzira zavyo"
  36,41,"N’ibimenyetso\tkuribo\tbimenyesha\tyuko\ttwajanye\tabavyeyi\tbabo mumato yari yuzuye mwo ibintu"
  36,42,Twabaremeye ivyo burira ko bimeze nkivyo bazo kurira ko
  36,43,Nitwa shaka twoshobora kuba somesha nturi kandi ntamufasha azoba arimwo canke uwuzoba rokora
  36,44,Atari kumpuhwe zivuye iwacu hamwe nukuba girira akamaro mukiringo kigufiya
  36,45,"Mugihe babwiwe bati:- nimutinye ibiri imbere yanyu hamwe n’ibiri inyuma yanyu kugira ngo muronke imihezagiro y’Imana"
  36,46,Ntakimenyetso icarico cose kibashikira mubimenyetso vy’Umuremyi wabo atari uko batavyitaho
  36,47,"Mugihe babwiwe bati:- nimutange muvyo Imana yabahaye, bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri baca babwira abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bati:- mbega tubarishe ibifungurwa mubo Imana yishakiye wenyene mwebwe ntimurimwo atari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  36,48,"Nabo bavuga bati:- iri sango rizoba ryari nimwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  36,49,Ntaco barindira atari ijwi rimwe gusa rizo sokora imitima yabo mugihe bazoba bariko baratongana aba nabariya
  36,50,Kandi ntibazo shobora kuraga muri ico gihe canke ngo bashobore kugaruka ku bantu babo
  36,51,"Munyuma hazovuzwa inzamba, mukanya isase uzoca ubona bazutse bavuye muntatemwa zabo bagenda ningoga na ningoga bagenda ku Muremyi wabo"
  36,52,"Bavuga bati:- yo! mbega ni nde yatuzuye muntatemwa zacu, ibi nivyo twemerewe nayene imigisha nivyo bavuze vy’ukuri intumwa z’Imana"
  36,53,"Ntakizoba atari iborogo rimwe gusa, mukanya isase gusa bose bazoba bamaze gushengezwa imbere yacu"
  36,54,"Uwo musi rero umutima w’umwumwe wese ntuzohemukirwa n’ikintu nakimwe, kandi ntimuzo rihwa impembo iyariyo yose atari kuvyo mwahora mugira"
  36,55,Mu vy’ukuri abantu bo mw’ijuru kuri uno musi bari mubikorwa vyabo biba nezereza
  36,56,"Abo\tbantu\thamwe\tn’imiryango\tyabo\tbari\tmubitutu\tbegamiye kunyegamo z’iteka"
  36,57,"Bazoronkerayo ivyamwa, kandi baronkereyo ivyo bipfuza mwo vyose"
  36,58,"Amahoro\tgusa\tniryo\tjambo\trizoba\trivuye\tku\tMuremyi\twabo\tnyene imigisha"
  36,59,Uno musi nimwi tandukanye nabo bantu babi
  36,60,Mbega sinaba buriye mwebwe bantu yuko muto hirahira ngo musenge Shetani mu vy’ukuri n’umwansi wanyu ari k’umugaragaro
  36,61,Yuko mwonsenga jewe Mana yanyu kuko ariyo nziza igororotse
  36,62,Ntankeka Shetani yarazimije abantu benshi cane muri mwebwe mbega ico gihe nti mwiyumvira
  36,63,Rero uwu niwo wamuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu mwamye mwemererwa n’Imana yanyu y’ukuri
  36,64,Uno musi uri hejuru nimu winjire mwo kubera ubuhakanyi bwanyu
  36,65,Kuri uwo musi tuzoziba iminwa yabo hanyuma amaboko yabo atuganirire ateko amaguru yabo abe ivyabona kuvyo bamye n’ivyemezo n’amaguru yabo abe kuvyo bahora bagira
  36,66,"Iyo dushaka twari kunogora amaso yabo bakaguma birukira mumayira, mugabo izo nzira bazibone gute"
  36,67,"Iyo dushaka twari kubagira ibikoko ubwo nyene naho bari, rero ntibari gushobora kugenda iyo baja canke gusubira inyuma iyo bavuye"
  36,68,"Nuwo duhaye ubuzima burebure tumusubiza inyuma mw’ishusho ryiwe ryambere, mbega ibi vyose ntibabishira mubwenge bwabo"
  36,69,"Natwe ntitwa mwigishije amajambo y’ubuhizi kandi ntivyoba kuriwe, kandi ntiyari kuba iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu atari uko ari icibutso n’igitabu kigaragaza ibikenewe vyose k’umugaragaro"
  36,70,Kugira ngo atuze uwuri muzima muribo kandi hemezwe ijambo kubatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  36,71,Mbega ntibabona yuko twebwe twabaremeye muvyo amaboko yacu yagize hamwe n’ibikoko batunze
  36,72,Nivyo bikoko twarabi gamburukije rero murivyo birurirwa n’ibindi navyo biraribwa
  36,73,"No muri ivyo bikoko barabironkera mwo akamaro kenshi hamwe n’ibinyobwa, mbega nikuki badashima"
  36,74,"Bagumanye\tizindi\tMana\taho\tkugumana\tImana\ty’ukuri\tkugira\tngo bafashwe nabo"
  36,75,Ntibashobora kubafasha nabo arizo ngabo zabo ziba cungereye
  36,76,"Rero ntibigutere agahinda kubera amajambo yabo, ntankeka twebwe dufise ubumenyi bw’ivyo banyegeza hamwe nivyo basemerera"
  36,77,"Mbega\tumuntu\tntazi\tyuko\ttwamuremye\tmw’Ima\try’intanga?\tnone yabaye mukeba wacu ari k’umugaragaro"
  36,78,"Yaradutangiyeko akarorero aribagira ukuremwa kwiwe aca avuga ati:- ni nde azozura amagufa y’abantu mugihe azoba yamaze kuvungagurika"
  36,79,"Vuga uti:- uwuzo yazura nurya yayaremye ubwambere, nawe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwukurema ibiremwa vyose"
  36,80,Niyo yabagiriye umukomezwa uvuye mugiti kibisi mukaba kuri ico giti namwe mucatsako
  36,81,"Mbega uwaremye Amajuru n’Isi mbega ntabushobozi afise bwukurema nk’aba yaremye, kubera iki nawe ari Umuremyi mukuru nyene ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  36,82,"Mu vy’ukuri itegeko ryiwe mugihe ishakiye ikintu icarico cose nukukibwira iti:- nube mumwanya isase kigaca kiba"
  36,83,"Aninahazwa ry’uwufise muminwe yiwe harimwo ubwami bw’ibintu vyose, niwe niho muzo subizwayo mwese"